Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,片名《叫我第一名》\NFront of the class
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫布莱德·科恩\NMy name is Bradley Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的小时候，人们还叫我很多别的“名字”\NBut when l was a kid, people called me by lots of names.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟杰夫叫我“波波医生”\NMy brother, Jeff, called me Dr. Bobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈叫我“宝贝”\NMy mom called me honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,学校的同学呢\NAnd the kids at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什么的都有：“神经病”、“怪胎”等等\NWell, they called me everything from spaz to freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我没什么朋友\NI didn't have many friends actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但却有个形影不离的伙伴一直陪着我\NBut I did have a constant companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,自从他来了后，我就想不起他有不在我身边的时候\NI can barely remember a time, when it wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有时他不会给我带来麻烦\NNow sometimes, it wasn't a problem for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有时，就会\NOther times, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,丢掉什么？丢掉书？\NDrop what? Drop books?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！\NStop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你紧张吗，布莱德？你有什么毛病吗？\NAre you scared Brad? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 少来烦我\NLeave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,打! 打! 打!\NFight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们在干嘛！\NWhat is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来啊，有种就来打！   - 住手！\N-Com'on. Bring it on!  - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不许再打了！住手！都回去上课！\NStop that fighting right now! Stop! Get back to class!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别胡闹了，你的麻烦大啦！\NStop that nonsense. You are in big trouble, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“女孩掉进泥巴里弄脏了”\NThe girl fell in the mud and got dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我忠诚的伙伴有个共识，那就是我们都讨厌学校\NOne thing my Constant Companion and, I agreed on was that we hated school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我等不及想走掉\NI couldn't wait until I got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不用再写作业，不用再看书，不用再看老师难看的脸色\NNo more homework, no more books, no more teachers' dirty looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的伙伴是在我6岁时出现的\NMy Companion first showed up, when I was six
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是过了很多年，他才有了个名字\Nbut it was years before it had a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但在眼下，精神科医生说我只是亢奋多动\NNow the shrinks said I was just hyper;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会发出怪声和做怪动作，来让自己吸引到注意\NI made funny noises and acted, weird to draw attention to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一个过渡期，我长大以后就会恢复正常\NIt was just a phase: I'd grow out of it and be "normal"....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟别人一样\N...like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来，这个伴儿一直跟着我\NThrough it all, my constant companion stuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的朋友只是觉得，我本来就是这样\NNow, to my friends, I'm just regular, ole Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“老布莱德”——喜欢棒球，爱听80年代的老歌\NThe guy who likes baseball. And who loves cheesy 80's music.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们觉得这比我发出的怪声更怪\NWhich they think is much weirder, than the noises I make.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好警官，我超速了吗？\NAfternoon, officer. Was I speeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,超过速限12哩\NTwelve miles over the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,圣路易？你是观光客？\NSt. Louis, huh? You a tourist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我住在亚特兰大，刚搬来这里\NNo, I live in Atlanta now, I just moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才大概有点分心吧\NI guess I was a little distracted...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小子，你喝酒了？\NSon, you been drinking...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，警官。我有“图雷特氏综合症”\NNo. No, sir.I have Tourette Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张，请你在这里签名\NTake it easy, son. I'm going to need you to sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你要找什么样的工作？\NSo. What kind of job you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,教书\NTeaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我想当老师\NI'm going to be a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常看到这种表情\NI get that look a lot;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但我从来不放在心上\Nbut I never let it get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你有布莱德利大学的学士学位\NI see you've got a B.A. from Bradley University -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是在伊利诺依州吧？\Nthat's in Illinois, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的\NYes, ma'am !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,毕业成绩优异，推荐度很高\NGraduated cum laude, high recommendations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的教学成果评估非常优异，好极了\Nyour student teaching evals are outstanding, excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会决定要教书？\NWhat made you decide to go into teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在想教书，我觉得我天生是老师的料\NIt's all I've ever wanted to do. I feel like I was born to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么选择来亚特兰大？\NWhy choose Atlanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说…你的家乡在密苏里州\NI mean...Missouri's your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想当勇士队的球迷，所以……\NI'm thinking of becoming a Braves fan.So, ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治亚州承认我的伊利诺伊州的教学执照\NGeorgia honors my Illinois teaching certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，我来这里当营队辅导员时\NPlus I fell in love with Atlanta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢上了亚特兰大\Nwhen I worked down here as a camp counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我就住这里\NI live here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲和我继母也住这里\NSo does my Dad and my Stepmom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能得到家人的支持\NWell, it's nice to have family here to...give you support.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是来谈谈“大象”吧\NMaybe we should talk about the elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大象？\NElephant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这屋子里的“大象”，我的图雷特氏症\NIn the room: my Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，根据美国残障保护法案，我不能问你…\NNo. The Americans with Disabilities Act doesn't allow me to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，但我想告诉你，就像我想告诉我的学生一样\NI know, but I'd like to tell you  - just like I tell the kids in my classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他们解释这是大脑方面的问题\NSee, I explain to them that it's a brain thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,导致让我发出奇怪的声音——就像打喷嚏一样控制不了\Nthat causes me to make strange noises --they're like sneezes, irrepressible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你想打喷嚏就非打不可\NWhen you have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,非打不可\Nyou have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,学生都有什么回应？\NHow do they react?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们明白以后就接受了\NOnce they understand, they're fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在课堂上这些从来不是问题\NIt's never caused any problems in a classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想得到一个机会\NAll I want is a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,能去面试的机会\NJust get me the interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,向他们证明我能胜任这个工作\Nand let me prove to them that I can do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,美国残障保护法案明文规定，我有权利得到这样的机会\NThe Americans with Disabilities Act says I'm entitled to a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,罗恩！\NRon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，情况怎么样？\NHey, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说：谁想要像狗叫的老师\NOh, you know: "Who wants a teacher that barks like a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我去找其他行当的工作\NYou should try another line of work."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没看你的履历？\NDidn't they look at your resume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你在开我玩笑啦\NYou're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会安排我跟几位校长面试\NThey're setting up interviews with some principals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了，什么时候？\N- Fantastic! - When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，我要等他们的电话\NOh, I don't know. I've gotta wait for their calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,换衣服，我们去庆祝一下\NGet changed - we gotta go celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是有约会吗？\NHaven't you got a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我看她能不能带个朋友一起来\NI'll see if she's got a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你也该认识几个女生了\NIt's about time you started meeting some chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在没心情交女朋友\NI can't focus on dating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有人说过你顽固透顶？\NHas anybody ever tell you you're obsessive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,每个我去看过的精神科医生都这么说\NOnly every shrink I ever saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那你保持这可笑的专注吧\NWell, have fun focusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸又打电话来了\NOh -- your Dad called again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你有空还是给他回个电话吧\NMaybe you should call him back,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好，回见\NAll right. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,给我爸回电话？\NReturning Dad's call?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得作好准备才行\NI'd have to prepare for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爸和妈在我很小的时候就离婚了\NSee, Mom and Dad had divorced when I was a little kid and my relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我爸的关系一直都……怎么说？挺复杂吧\Nwith Dad had always been - umm, let's just say -- complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我磨光了他的耐性，就像黑板上的钉子一样\NI mean, I wore out his patience like nails on a chalkboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,更糟的是我弟弟杰夫也有点多动\NIt didn't help that my brother Jeff was also a little hyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸说他要赶着回亚特兰大的家\NDad said he's waiting to get back to his home in Atlanta,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他想跟你说再见\Nhe's waiting to say goodbye -
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再见！\NGoodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你会惹他生气啦\NYou're gonna make him mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来，我们比赛！\NCome on -- I'll race you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想跟我比？门儿都没有\NAgainst The Green Dragon? You gotta be kidding --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 笨蛋！\NSucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你作弊！\NCheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抄捷径！\NShort cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你骑脚踏车耶！\NYou got a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了，杰夫\NSee you, Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平啦\NHey! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来啊！\NAw, com'on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰夫\NJeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢不了我啦\NYou're not going to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看，我就要赢了\NSee, I'm gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平！你骑脚踏车！\NThat's not fair! You got a bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不准你这样！不！你作弊！\NOh, no you're not! Oh, no! You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙！小声点啦\NHey guys! quiet down, you guys, quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别吵到邻居了 - 过来\NWe do have neighbors you know. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看吧，我赢了\NSee, I did beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来。布莱德，过来亲爱的，请你专心一点好吗？\NYeah. Calm down. Brad, com'ere. Com'on honey, focus, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,过来，过来这里，站好了\NCom'ere. Come here! Stand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，听我说，请你专心好吗？\NListen. Listen up. Focus, please. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们帮我一个忙\NI need you guys to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩要多体谅妈妈，OK？\NI want you both to make life a little easier for your mom, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快把她搞疯了…听好！住手！布莱德！\NYou are driving her nuts. Guys, listen! Hey, hey. Stop it! Brad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要帮忙她做家务事\NHelp her out around the house;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先，不能再有这些烦人的举动了，好吗？\Nbut most of all let us stop the obnoxious behavior, OK? --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，听着，我是认真的！\NHey, listen. I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别再闹了！\NOK? Quit the clowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟觉得好玩，但我不觉得！\NYour brother may think its funny, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制不了嘛\NI can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你可以的\NYes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只要稍微控制一点就行了\NThere's nothing wrong with you that a little self-control wouldn't fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，停下！\NNow, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 诺曼？  - 什么事？\N-Norman?  -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 飞机可是不等人的哦\NThey're not going to hold that plane for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好，好了，抱一下\NOkay, all right. Gimme a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸，再见\NSee you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见了，小杰米\NBye-bye, J-man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸，我爱你\NI love you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也爱你\NLove you too, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听好了，下次去我家住吧，怎么样？\NHey, listen up; we'll stay at my house next time. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好，我带你们去看勇士队的球赛\NOK! I'll get tickets to a Braves' game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，记住刚才我们讲的\NAnd Brad, remember what we talked about:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要自制一点，好吗？\NSelf-control. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈，需要帮忙吗？\N- Need any help with anything, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 既然你提到了就来帮忙吧\N- Well...now that you mention it....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,离婚后，我和杰夫帮忙妈妈创业\NAfter the divorce, Jeff and I helped Mom with her new business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她在四处兜售精品高级服饰\NSort of a high class traveling boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可能也不算是帮忙啦\NWell, maybe helped isn't exactly the right word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,艾伦，这些衣服好漂亮\NOh, Ellen, these things are exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在圣路易找不到这种流行款式\NYou never find styles like this in St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是直接从加州来的，比佛利山庄\NWell, it is direct from California. Beverly Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都这样穿\NThis is what everyone is wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这件。孩子们？孩子们！\NLook at this. Boys? Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,躲猫猫？\NHide and seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开始数\NCount.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 1\NOne...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,艾伦，我不想看两位数大码的衣服\NNow, Ellen, I don't want to see anything in double-digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，加州的东西都偏小\NOh, honey, everything in California runs small.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你试穿看看\NGo ahead. Just try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，能请你冷静下来吗？\NBrad, would you please calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他像狗一样吠耶！\NHe's barking like a dog, for goodness sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看\NNow look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,请别误会\NDon't take this the wrong way -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是把你当朋友才说这些的\Nyou know I wouldn't say this to you if we weren't friends -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有考虑过找人驱魔？\Nbut have you considered an exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你还是要面对现实，你的尺寸是12号\NYou know, I think you might have to face. the fact that you're a size 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得不好，我帮你剪标\NI can cut the label, if it makes you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个新医生，听听他怎么说好吗\NIt's a new doctor; let's just listen to what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我都知道他会说什么了\NI know what he'll have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你因为离婚的事生你妈的气吗？布莱德\NDo you feel any anger toward your mother,because of the divorce, Brad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没，没有\NNo. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你因为爸爸不跟你住而生他气吗？\NDo you resent your father because he doesn't live with you anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,爸妈离婚你会自责吗？\NDo you blame yourself for the divorce, Brad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我还很小，我甚至都记不清了\NIt happened when I was a little kid, I don't even remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩太太，布莱德无法接受父母离婚\NMrs. Chen, Brad has some serious denial issues regarding the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,需要在家里要给他划定很明确的界限\NWhat he needs at home are some clear boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要让他明白这样的行为完全无法被接受\NHe needs to understand that this behavior is totally unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而这，就是你的职责了，科恩太太\NAnd that, Mrs. Cohen, is your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最难过的就是我让妈妈很辛苦\NThe hardest part was knowing how tough I made things for Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在尽量帮她忙了\NI tried as best as I could for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要记得给他按时吃药\NMake sure he keeps taking his medication, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,至于我爸？\NAnd for Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,三振！\NStrike three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我打棒球\NI played sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在球场上，我是如鱼得水\NOn the ball field, I fit right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说，每个打棒球的人都会发出怪声，做一些奇怪的动作\NI mean, everybody makes funny noises and has strange tics at a baseball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,波波加油！\NGo, Bobo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德加油！快！\NCome on, Brad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，要点什么？\NAll right. What can l get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了，我有好消息要告诉你们\NHey, guys. I got something pretty exciting to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别吃这么快，你会打嗝的\NHoney, don't eat so fast. You're gonna get the hiccups.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他老是在打嗝\NHe's always got the hiccups.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你才打嗝咧\NYou're a hiccup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了，你别这么激动好吗？\NListen, hey! Would you just relax?.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈说你一直都没吃药\NMom says you're not taking your meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你怎么会…你怎么能冷静下来？\NHow are you ever...how are you ever going to calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你都不按医生说的去做\Nif you don't do what the doctor tells you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,吃药只会更严重的啦\NPills just make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗，现在你才是医生吗？\NOh I see. So you're a doctor now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他是波波医生\NHe's Dr. Bobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴！\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，我们吃东西吧\NAll right, guys, let's eat, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我有重要的消息要宣布，听我说\NI have a very important announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们？孩子们！好，闹够了，回车上去，走吧\NGuys? Guys! All right. That's it. We're going back to the car. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我还饿呢\NI'm still hungry --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我想怎样吗？希望你有一天不要胡闹\NYou know what would be nice? One day without you acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一天就好了\NOne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，等等我！\NWait up, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要宣布什么事，爸？\NSo, what's the announcement, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我有新对象了\NI've been seeing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“新对象”是什么意思？\NWhat do you mean seeing somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫黛安，她…\NHer name is Diane, and she....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，请你别再这样\NBrad, please! Stop doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我没办法\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是，还没决定什么啦，但...\NI mean, nothings' happened yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想不想会有个继母？\Nhow would you guys feel about having a stepmom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,才不！\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经有妈妈了\NWe've already got a Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在会有两个啊\NWell. Now you're gonna have two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你妈说了，她不介意，她说…\NI talked to your mom about it and she's fine with it. She said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你别再这样！停下！\NI said STOP It! STOP It!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸发脾气我不怪他\NSee, I really couldn't blame Dad for losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的怪动作把他搞疯了\NMy tics drove him nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他也跟我的老师一样，不知道我为什么会有奇怪的行为\NBecause, like my teachers, he had no name for my strange behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只知道这是“无法容忍”的\NExcept "insufferable".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么，我的成绩还可以\NNow, somehow -- I don't know how --I made okay grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但正常人要做一个小时的事，我需要两个小时\NBut, what would take a normal person an hour, took me two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至三个小时，我喜欢学习，但我讨厌念书\NOr three. I mean, I loved learning, but I hated, hated reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我一专心，那个忠诚的伙伴就会捣蛋\NTrying to concentrate brought out the worst in my Constant Companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德？请你过来\NBrad? Come up here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你爱耍宝，但我受够你了\NI know you think you're the class clown, but I've had it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能…控制…控制不了\NI can't - help -help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你每次都这样讲，我不想再听什么借口了\NThat's what you always say. I don't want to hear any more excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,同学们想念书…\NYour classmates are trying to study...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样闹腾会妨碍他们\N...and your clowning makes it impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我道歉，你要跟他们道歉\NDon't apologize to me. Apologize to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同学，看这边，请你们坐好\NEyes up here, everyone. Sit up straight, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德有话要跟你们说\NBrad has something to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我……\NI'm sorry l...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,害得你们没办法念书\Nthat you can't study because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢？\NAnd?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要保证不再发出怪声了\NYou promise never to make any more silly noises ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证不会再发出怪声\NPromise I won't make any more silly noises ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,回去坐好，大家继续看书\NTake your seat. All of you, back to your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这些对你来说也许很艰难\NAs difficult as this may be for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩太太，你也许很难接受，但老师们都无计可施了\NMrs. Cohen, I assure you, the teachers are at their wits end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然我能理解…     - 莎伦，我不接任何电话\N-I understand that, of course... - Sharon, would you hold all my calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我们只能…\N...but all we...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是最后一次机会了，真的是最后一次\NNow, this has got to be the last chance. The very last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，我找你妈妈来\NBrad, look, I sent for your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在学校的状况很失控\Nbecause things have just gotten out of control here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天她要带你回家。你可以再来上学…\NNow, she's going to take you home today. You can come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制不了\NCan't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，你说什么？\NSorry, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他控制不了\NHe said he can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果他说的是实话呢？\NWhat if he's telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子很聪明，科恩太太，但你再替他找借口…\NYou've got a bright boy, Mrs. Cohen,but making excuses for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,替他找借口是帮不了他的\NMaking excuses is not going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他需要在这段时间里问下自己…\NNow, he needs to use this time to ask himself ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布莱德，我们走吧\NBrad! Com'on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,问他自己为何要自毁前程\N...this question: "Why am I sabotaging myself?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就算被退学也无所谓，我讨厌那所学校\NI don't care if they expel me. I hate that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不管哪一所学校都一样啦\NWell, it's that school or another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌所有的学校。我们来这里干嘛？\NI hate all schools. Why are we going here -- ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,来找答案\NTo find some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能进图书馆，他们会把我赶出来。求求你\NI can't go in the library --they'll throw me out. Please, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，你过来，坐这儿\NAll right, com'ere. Sit over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许是我们方向错了\NWell, maybe we're just going down the wrong track.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁？\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大家\NAll of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我！\NGet off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吉娃娃…\NWet Willie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 极刑！不要极刑啦！\NOh no, wet Willie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很忙，诺曼，我不会占用你太多的时间\NI know you're busy, Norman, I won't take up much of your time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想告诉你…\Nbut I really think you should hear this --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们，小声一点，我在跟爸爸讲话\NBoys, keep it down --I'm trying to talk to your Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要跟他讲话\NI wanna talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等一下！小声！\NIn a minute! Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，那些老师和那个医生\NListen. You know,those teachers and that doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都觉得是父母不尽责\Nto them it's all about bad parenting which, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,其实也就是指我，因为我是单亲\Ncomes down to me because I'm the only one who here -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在怪你，诺曼\NNo. I'm not blaming you, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我是不想再自责了\NIn fact, I'm going to stop blaming myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟一位朋友聊过，她认为是医生诊断有误\NI was talking to a friend and she think the doctors are missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我去图书馆借了一堆医学书\NI got this stack of medical books from the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈，小心！    - 我做了些…\N-Mom, watch out! -And, I've been doing a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,研究…\Nresearch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别再说他欠管教了，诺曼！\NStop saying he just needs more discipline, Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管做什么都不能让他…\NNothing I do helps -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他控制不了自己，我也无计可施\NHe is out of control and I'm at the end of my rope -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以跟爸爸讲话吗？\NCan I talk to Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能等一会？\NCan you just wait a minute, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈！\NMOM!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，讲完再叫我听\NAll right. But give him back to me when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，杰夫？\NWhat is it, Jeffrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，爸爸\NHey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对，那场比赛很精彩，我两次安打和一次四坏球\NYeah, it was a great game;I got two base hits and a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，妈，我给你添麻烦了\NSorry I cause you so much trouble, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这本书找到这些，你念念看\NI want you to read something in this book I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是本医学书，这些也许能解释你为何一直发出怪声\NIt's a medical book that might explain why you make all those noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌念书，妈…\NI hate reading, Mom --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,念吧\NRead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,图雷特氏综合症\N"Tourette Syndrome."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德不就是这样吗？发出怪声和抽动…\NThat, that's Brad, isn't it? The noises and the twitches....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要进一步检查，但也许你是对的\NI'll still need to do more tests but, umm, you could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的方向可能错了\NWe may have been headed down the wrong road, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没遇过图雷特氏症的病例\NI've never actually seen a case of Tourette's before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我多年的伴儿终于有了名字\NSo at last my Constant Companion had a name....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这本书上写说无药可医，但也许现在有了，这本书很旧\NThis says there's no cure. But that may have changed. This is an old book --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还是没有，科恩太太，我很抱歉\NThat hasn't changed, Mrs. Cohen. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，但医学界还在研究对吧？总有一天会找到的\NYeah, but they're still looking for a cure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说，总有一天会找到的，不是吗？\NI mean, they will find one, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们…他们得找…\NThey - they...have to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了，妈，我们会好的，都会好的。\NIt's OK, Mom. We'll get through this, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\NOh, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看，所以这是有原因的，爸\NSEE? There's a reason, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意在捣蛋\NJoop, joop, I'm not being weird on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，我…\NListen, uh, Brad. l, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，我要说的话都说完了，再见\NAll right. Well, it's all I wanted to say. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸终于相信我了，但他对我没信心\NFinally, my dad believed me. But he never believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不相信我会成功，不相信我能教书\NThat I would succeed.That I could teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂？我是布莱德\NHello, this is Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有狗？对，那是我的狗\NA dog? Ahh, yes. Yes, ma'am, that's my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，好，早上11点我可以到\NAhh, OK. Yes. Yes, I can be there 11am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的第一次面试…\NMy very first interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，我没问题。好，谢谢你\NGreat. That sounds great. OK. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽量不要反应过度，我克制了身体的抽动\NI tried not to over-react. I help in my tics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！太好了！\NYES! Waffle, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个电话之后，我又接到两个：三位校长，三次面试机会\NAfter that first call, I got two more: three interviews with three principals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,无需多说，我这位多年的伙伴真是满腔热诚\NNeedless to say, my Constant Companion was more than a little enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，你只拿到了学士学位\NWell, I see you only your bachelor's degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你有打算修硕士吗？\NAre you planning to get your Master's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有的，先生，一有机会我就去\NYes, sir. JOOP! As soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，这不是必备条件啦\NWell, we don't require it for entry level...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但，如果你是认真想…    - 我很认真\N-but if you're serious about... -I'm very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把教书当终身职业\NI want to make teaching my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:22:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我发出这些怪声，是因为我有图雷特氏综合症\NI, ahh, I make these noises because I have Tourette Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你聊这件事\NI'd like to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是神经失调，我的大脑传送混乱的讯息给我的身体\NIt's a Neurological disorder where my brain sends mixed signals to my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就像打喷嚏一样，无法控制\NIt's like a sneeze. It's irrepressible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,过一、两个礼拜我再回复你\N... a couple of weeks,and I'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 - 好，谢谢你\N-OK! -OK. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢   - 你保重\N-Thanks. - Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，一振出局\NWell. Strike one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但我妈妈说过，不要轻言放弃\NBut, like Mom always said, don't ever give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候，我妈从来没停止研究\NWhen I was little, Mom never stopped researching because,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为虽然我无药可医，但也许有办法过正常生活\Nwhile there was no cure, there might be ways to live a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妈，这是教堂\NIt's a church, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝，不是要你去上圣经课啦\NHoney, you're not going to have to get a Bible lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是个互助团体\NThis is just a support group.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我非去不可吗？\NDo I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要多和其他图雷特氏症患者接触\NYou need to connect with other people who have Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他们是怎么过日子的，好不好？\NFind out how they live with it. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去试试看\NLet's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要进去\NI'm not going in there --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝…\NHoney...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没看过图雷特氏症患者\NI'd never seen anyone with Tourette's before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有人是眨眼睛和鼻子抽动\NThere were eye blinkers and nose twitchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有人是踏脚和颈部抽动，有人会大叫和咳嗽\NFoot stompers and neck jerkers. Some of them yelped and coughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.30,0:23:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我在别人眼里就是这样吗？\NIs this what I looked like to other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，波波，我们是来学习的。开始学习吧\NCome on, Bobo. We're here to learn. Let's start learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,美国残障法案给我们权利\NThe Americans with Disabilities Act gives us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,做想做的事或去想去的地方\Nthe right to do anything or go anyplace that we want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但你去看电影试试看\NBut try going to a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,或是去音乐会或餐厅\NOr a concert or a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别人大吼着要你闭嘴，这时候法律根本没意义\NThat law doesn't mean anything when people are yelling at you to shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我一回到家，爸妈就关窗户，拉上百叶窗\NI come home and my parents close the windows and blinds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们不想让邻居看到我的症状\Nbecause they don't want the neighbors to see me tic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没人尝试着要被人接受\NNo one was even trying to be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大人都没工作，小孩都待在家\NThe audits were out of work.The kids stayed at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:23:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我可以确定\NI knew one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想跟他们一样\NI didn't want to be like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:24:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就连他球队的教练都不接受他\NEven the coaches on his team wouldn't accept him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了\NOh, I'd had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也是在家自学吧？\NOf course, you're home-schooling, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，布莱德和其他小孩一样上学\NNo. Brad goes to school like any other kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这些小孩和别的小孩不一样，上学对他们来说是浪费时间\NThese kids are not like any other kids;school's a waste of time for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他三年级我就让他休学了，免得我失去理智\NI took him out at the third grade just to save my sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的劝\NYou want my advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.93,0:24:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你也照做吧\N...you'll do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.30,0:24:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好，谢谢你\NYep. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.03,0:24:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,波波，我们走\NLet's go, Bobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.44,0:24:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是互助团体！哪里互助了？\NIt's supposed to be a support group! Where's the support?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.54,0:24:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,难道要一辈子躲在家里吗？\NSupposed to just hide away for the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.18,0:24:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我不该带你来这里，宝贝，忘了他们吧\NI'm really so sorry that I brought you there, honey, let's just forget this --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.21,0:24:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妈，我不想忘了\NI don't want to forget this, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人向图雷特氏症投降，但我是绝对不会放弃的\NThose people let Tourette's win. I'm never gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.25,0:24:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很难想像当时我才12岁\NIt's difficult to imagine that at the age of twelve
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就领悟了人生真正的道理\NI would find a genuine philosophy to live by.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.69,0:24:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但这就是那一刻，决定性的一刻\NBut here it was. This defining moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.43,0:25:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要永远都正面迎战逆境\NTo always face my adversity head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.13,0:25:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下次去面试前，我决定更坦白一点\NWhen I went to my next interview, I decided to be even more up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.80,0:25:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,先把我有图雷特氏症的事讲清楚\NGet the Tourette's stuff out of the way first
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.91,0:25:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再把我的教学理念告诉对方\Nand then dazzle 'em with my approach to teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.54,0:25:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,从你的资料看来做得很成功\Nyou seem to have been very successful
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.34,0:25:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有图雷特氏症，\N...in spite of your Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.51,0:25:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我很努力地想当个好老师\NI've worked very hard to become the best teacher I can be --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.25,0:25:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你抽空过来，我再通知你\NThank you for coming in.I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.98,0:25:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.95,0:25:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白也没用啦\NSo much for being up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.99,0:25:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我第三次面试\NFor my third interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.02,0:25:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定完全不提我的图雷特氏症\NI decided to discussing about my Tourette's at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.73,0:25:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我每个礼拜都会寄进度报告给每位学生的家长\NEach week I like to send home a progress report to my students' parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.96,0:25:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望学生在学习过程中要多发表意见\NUm, I like to give my students a voice in their learning --to be hands-on...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.20,0:25:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在课堂上要实践和互动\Nand interactive in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.14,0:25:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也要让家长密切参与\Nbut also to keep the parents closely involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.81,0:25:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,罗恩，不提我的图雷特氏症是一大失策\NRon, it was a huge mistake not mentioning my Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.48,0:25:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这就表示我想掩饰\NIt was, you know, I was trying to hide it --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.42,0:25:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没希望了啦\NFat chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.72,0:25:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧，这是负面想法\NOkay, that's the negative --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.19,0:25:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不，你别再给自己压力了，你都压得我喘不过气了\NNo. The negative is you've gotta stop stressing out. You're stressing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.29,0:26:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但正面的态度是\NBut the positive is that, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别人好像不太在意嘛\Nthe others didn't seem to have a problem with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.10,0:26:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是要等电话\NI just, I gotta wait for a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.46,0:26:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,正面的态度是你要跟我出去\NThe positive is you're coming out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.93,0:26:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的新女友有位室友\NMy new girlfriend -she has a roommate --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.07,0:26:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能别再帮我牵线？\NWill you stop trying to set me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.31,0:26:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等我准备好了就会去约会啦\NWhen I am ready to date, I will date.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.54,0:26:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，你的事她都听说了，她还是想认识你\NCome on, she heard all about you; she still wants to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.34,0:26:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，多谢你的好意。听着，我想放松一下。好吗？\NOh thanks. Real kind. Listen, I want to relax. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.28,0:26:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看勇士队比赛\NI want to watch the Braves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.52,0:26:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都想看勇士队比赛，去换衣服啦\NWe all want to watch the Braves. Get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.19,0:26:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,罗恩跟我说你正在积极找工作\NSo, Ron tells me that you're on a big job hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.33,0:26:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,进展得怎样？\NHow's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错\NAhh, pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.23,0:26:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只是还没人录用我啦\NExcept no one's hired me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.73,0:26:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们大概是在抢着要我去吧\NI guess they're all too busy fighting to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.04,0:26:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会这样？\NYou do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.51,0:26:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,给我留下了深刻的印象\NI'm impressed by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.74,0:26:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 本来就是    - 没想到你也会这样\N-You should be.  -I was not expecting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.74,0:26:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,了不起\NThat's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.91,0:26:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我很厉害\NBut I'm pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是啊\NYou are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.88,0:26:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是运动迷？\NSo you are really a sports fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.08,0:27:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对，超迷的，足球、垒球、网球\NAh, yes. Big time.Soccer, softball...tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.32,0:27:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我大学时代经常运动，但还达不到职业水准啦\NYep, I played a lot in college, but I'm not good enough for the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.43,0:27:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是，但我想跟他一样棒\NI hear that because I wish I was good enough to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.93,0:27:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟谁？\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.93,0:27:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他\NHim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你想当吉祥物？\NOh, you want to be a mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.30,0:27:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他叫荷马…          - 荷马\N-His name is Homer... -Homer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.30,0:27:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我毕生的抱负\NAnd it's a lifelong ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.61,0:27:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧\NOK. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.84,0:27:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别转过去看      - 好\N-Don't look now.  -OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.21,0:27:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在别看，我们后面有个家伙\NDon't look now, but there's this guy behind us
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.18,0:27:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他哪根筋不对，他一直盯着你看\Nand I don't know what his problem is.He keeps staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.42,0:27:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常看到那种表情\NAhh. I actually get that look a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.59,0:27:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是羡慕的眼神\NIt's a look of envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.99,0:27:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他在想要怎么跟我一样，发出这么酷的声音？\NHe's thinking, "How can l make cool noises like that guy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.36,0:27:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你还满乐观面对你的…\NYou have such a great attitude about your...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.30,0:27:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,荷马再见！再见！  - 再见了，罗恩\NBye Homer! Bye. Bye, Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:27:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.21,0:28:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,荷马再见！勇士队加油！\NBye, Homer! Go, Braves!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.01,0:28:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,进展得不错嘛，你有再约她出来吗？\NSo that must have gone well, huh? Did you ask her out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.45,0:28:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有，我约了，但我有第二次约会综合症\NYeah, I asked. But, it's second date syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.75,0:28:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我人很好，她也很风趣，只是…\NYou know, I'm a great guy, she had a lot of fun, but, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.22,0:28:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你那些症状酷到她难以招架？\NYour tics are just too cool for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.82,0:28:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦，她说是因为我室友口臭\NActually, no, she says because my roommate's breath smells so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.73,0:28:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么意思？\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.56,0:28:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你明知故问\NYou know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.11,0:28:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我是布莱德，嗨，爸\NThis is Brad. Ahh, hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.74,0:28:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，罗恩跟我说你打给我\NYeah, no, Ron --Ron told me you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.61,0:28:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我最近都忙着…\NI just, ahh, you know, I've been so busy that, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.78,0:28:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没吃午饭\NNo. I haven't had lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.79,0:28:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好，没问题，你想约在哪儿？\NAll right, that sounds great. Where do you want to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.63,0:28:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在爸爸工作的地方吃午饭\NLunch at Dad's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.19,0:28:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他就不必担心我发出怪声了\NHe wouldn't have to worry about my noises there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.60,0:28:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还要再加桁架再跟我说，好吗？\NLet me know if you need any more of those trusses, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.84,0:29:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.67,0:29:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨\N-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨，爸爸    - 你找到这里了\NHey, Dad. See you found your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.74,0:29:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.11,0:29:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去我办公室外面吃午饭吧，那里比较隐私一点\NLet's grab lunch outside my office. Be a little more private.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.51,0:29:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.51,0:29:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,黛安在问你几时会来我们家\NDiane's wondering when you're gonna come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.12,0:29:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你大概在忙着找工作吧，有进展吗？\NI guess you've been pretty busy with the job hunt. Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.15,0:29:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还在面试\NStill interviewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.32,0:29:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,面试得如何？\NHow's that going?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.26,0:29:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有没有介意你的…\NAre they giving you any trouble with your, uh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.26,0:29:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以说出来…图雷特氏症\NYou can say the word, Dad: Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.60,0:29:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人介意，有些人不会\NSome of them are. Some of them aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.67,0:29:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的钱还够用吧？\NHow's your money holding out?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不是来找你要钱的\NI'm not asking you for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.60,0:29:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，你从来不跟我要东西\NI know that.You never ask me for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.31,0:29:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.71,0:29:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但你缺钱随时可以来我这边工作\NBut if you ever do get short,you know you gotta job with me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.61,0:29:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸，我要教书\NI'm going to teach, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.28,0:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.18,0:29:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让任何事妨碍我做到\NI can't let anything get in the way of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.28,0:29:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我只是觉得多点选择也没什么不好\NOK. I'm jut saying there's nothing wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.45,0:29:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,免得有些事屡试不成时\N...with keeping your options open in case things don't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.25,0:29:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看，除了教书之外还有很多其他工作\NYou know, there are other things besides teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.32,0:29:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,都不适合我\NNot for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.76,0:29:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸永远不懂我的乐观\NDad could never understand my optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.53,0:29:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像我小学毕业时\NLike when I graduated to middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常希望情况能有所改观\NI was really hopeful that things would be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.76,0:30:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，布莱德？一个人吃饭？\NWhat's the matter Brad? Eat alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.83,0:30:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,新的开始，新的学校, 新的朋友\NMake a fresh start. New school. New friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.27,0:30:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,结果却一样\NSame result.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.01,0:30:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们要教的是分数\NToday, we're going to be talking about fractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.61,0:30:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,分数是你的好朋友\NFractions are your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.01,0:30:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,日常生活中经常用到分数\NUse fractionsin every day life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.15,0:30:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是不了解它\NYou just don't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.32,0:30:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比如你妈妈烤了一个馅饼\NFor example, say your mother bakes a pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.52,0:30:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她把馅饼切成几份\NShe cuts that pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.16,0:30:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩，你去校长室\NCohen! Just go to the principal's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.53,0:30:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是跟校长自我介绍的好方法\NNot the best way to introduce myself to the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.65,0:30:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，你觉得学校是干什么的地方？\NWhat do you think a school's for, Brad?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.99,0:30:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉，我一直打断课程…\NI'm sorry I keep disrupting the class --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.32,0:30:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没回答我的问题，学校是干嘛的？\NYou're not answering my question. What's a school for?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.36,0:31:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要教育学生，不是吗？\NTo educate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.89,0:31:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要用知识来打败无知\NTo use knowledge to wipe out ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.07,0:31:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,学校的交响乐团今天下午有音乐会\NThe school orchestra's having a concert this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.07,0:31:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去吗？\NYou planning on going?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.87,0:31:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去，我这个样子会打扰演出的\NNo, sir. My tics will ruin the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.21,0:31:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你去\NI want you to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.01,0:31:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同学，请回座\NEverybody just keep your seats for a minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.31,0:31:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，音乐会好听吗？\NThank you. Did you enjoy the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.62,0:32:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,表现得很好\NGreat job.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.96,0:32:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安静的时候有没有听到怪声？\NDid you hear any noises during the quiet parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.06,0:32:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有\NYES!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.13,0:32:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我也有听到\NYeah. So did l.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.33,0:32:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还满讨厌的，对吧？\NThey're pretty annoying, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.33,0:32:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,发出那些怪声的人是布莱德·科恩\NThe person making those noises is Brad Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.41,0:32:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，你上台\NCome on up here, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.22,0:33:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢发出怪声惹人讨厌吗？\NDo you like making noises and upsetting people, Brad?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.85,0:33:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.56,0:33:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那你干嘛要这样？\NThen why do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.69,0:33:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我有图雷特氏综合症\NBecause I have Tourette Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.93,0:33:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.53,0:33:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我大脑有问题，所以会发出怪声\NIt's a thing in my brain that causes me to make weird noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.97,0:33:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但你想控制就能控制，对吧？\NBut you could control it if you wanted to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.41,0:33:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不对，这是一种病\NNo, sir. It's a sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.71,0:33:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么没接受治疗？\NWell, why can't you just get cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.45,0:33:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有药可以医\NThere isn't any cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.69,0:33:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不喜欢听到怪声，我也不喜欢发出怪声\NI don't like making noises any more than you like hearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.39,0:33:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我压力大的时候会更严重\NThey're even worse when I get stressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.19,0:33:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,比如你们无法接受我不能控制\Nwhen you don't accept that I can't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.26,0:33:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但大家都接受我，我就不会那么严重了\NBut when I feel accepted,then they're not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.50,0:34:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能怎么做？\NWhat can we do --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.14,0:34:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我指的是学校里的每一个人\Nand I mean everyone in this school -
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.35,0:34:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能怎么帮你，布莱德？\NWhat can we do to help you, Brad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.79,0:34:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望大家别用异样眼光看我\NI just want to be treated like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.36,0:34:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说得好，回去坐吧\NGood job. Go sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.96,0:35:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,几句话 —— 点拨一下\NA few words -- a little education -
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就像开启了通往全新世界的大门\Nand it was like opening a door to a brand new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.62,0:35:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我知道将来无论何时、何地\NNow some day, some way, I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.02,0:35:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,无论我有没有图雷特氏症\NTourette's or no Tourette's,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我都要当一个老师\NI was going to be a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.59,0:35:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我别无选择，只能证明图雷特氏症\NI had no choice but to prove that Tourette's would
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.79,0:35:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不会打倒我\Nnever get the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.86,0:35:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我放弃了，就等于是认同\Nlf I quit, I would be agreeingwith everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.59,0:35:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那些跟我说我想得太天真的人\Nwho ever told me I was barking up the wrong tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，空调坏了，早就应该修好啦\NSorry about the air conditioning.Supposed to already be fixed by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.07,0:35:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\NThat's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.18,0:35:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的履历还不错\NWell, umm, your resume looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.45,0:36:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们五年级也有个缺\NAnd we do have an opening in fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.85,0:36:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.19,0:36:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要告诉你，在这里教书可不轻松\NBut I do have to tell you:this is a tough place to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.46,0:36:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有几个头痛人物\NWe've got some really hard cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.23,0:36:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我视之为挑战\NWell, I take that as a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.39,0:36:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为有哪个小孩是没救的\NI don't believe that any kid is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.40,0:36:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都想学习，你永远不能放弃\NYou know, they all want to learn; you can't ever give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.23,0:36:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要...\NLet me just...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.20,0:36:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只是要找对方法教导他们\NYou just gotta find the right way to teach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.47,0:36:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你喉咙有痰吗？\NAhh, you got something stuck in your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.87,0:36:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要喝杯水？\NWould you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.37,0:36:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我有图雷特氏症。我想解释一下，\NI have Tourette Syndrome. I'd like to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.07,0:36:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它是一种神经上的…    - 图雷特氏症？\N-It's a neurological... - Tourette's?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.31,0:36:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是会骂脏话？\NIsn't that where you yell out obscenities?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.84,0:36:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是秽语症，这种症状很罕见\NThat's coprolalia,It's, ahh, it's a rare symptom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.68,0:36:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只有少部分的图雷特氏症患者会有\Nthat a small percentage of people with Tourette's have.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.25,0:36:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就没有这种症状    - 好吧，\N-I don't have that.  - OK, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.21,0:36:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没说你是身心障碍\NThey did not tell me that you were going to be handicapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.88,0:36:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算要怎么调教一群调皮的学生？\NHow do you expect to handle a bunch of wild students
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.19,0:36:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在有这方面残障的情况下？\Nwith a handicap like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.79,0:36:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，教育他们啊\NWell. By educating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.76,0:36:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们知道这是不必避讳的\NBy letting them know it's okay to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.99,0:36:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以提问题…                  - 这些学生会嘲笑你\N-It's okay to ask questions...  - These students would laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.03,0:36:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不会的…当他们明白\NNot...not when they understand
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.37,0:36:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这只是小状况…            - 好吧，我有看过\N-it's simply a matter of... - OK. I have seen teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.47,0:36:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有残疾的老师\Nwith disabilities before ...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.91,0:37:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,…但从来没遇过像你这种的\N...but never with what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.61,0:37:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是看不出你怎么能教一个班的学生\NI just don't see how you could ever teach a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.08,0:37:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我能教，你看我的履历\NI can teach! Look at my resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.22,0:37:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细看看！好吗？\NLook at it! Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.55,0:37:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我在教学上非常成功\NI was very successful as a student teacher -
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.09,0:37:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的图雷特氏症从来就不是问题\Nmy Tourette's never posed a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.96,0:37:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以教书\NI can teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.59,0:37:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，反正我需要五年级的老师\NOK. Bottom line: I need somebody now for fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.06,0:37:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在这里教书\NYou want to teach here,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.06,0:37:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在课堂上就不能发出怪声\Nyou're gonna have to refrain from making these noises in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.51,0:37:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你明白了吗？    - 谢谢你给我面试的机会\NYou know what?     - Thank you very much for the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.48,0:37:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是想要这份工作吗？\NBut, don't you want the job -- ?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我真的非常想要\NYes, actually. I want it really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.71,0:37:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但我再怎样也不替一个不关心他的学生的人工作\NBut I would never, ever work for a man who doesn't care about his students.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.15,0:37:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要把我的资料带走，不再浪费你宝贵的时间\NSo, I'll take my portfolio and, ahh, and take no more of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.82,0:37:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你老板人还真好啊\NYou got a great boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.64,0:38:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我最烂的一次面试经验\NWell, it was the worst interview I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.61,0:38:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他只看到我图雷特氏症的那一面\NAll he could see when he looked at me was my Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.75,0:38:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都只看到这一面\NThat's all any of them see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.05,0:38:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝，他们没看到你是个好老师\NWell, honey, if they can't see what a great teacher you'd be
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.15,0:38:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他们的损失，不是你的错\Nthat is their failure, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.39,0:38:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是我的错\NWell, it sure seems like my failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.36,0:38:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你要这么说，我也没办法啦\NWell, if you say so. You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然你干脆举白旗放弃，回家来吧，怎么样？\NWhy don't you just throw in the towel and come home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.40,0:39:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你买张机票\NI'll buy you a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.40,0:39:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我又没这样讲\NI'm not saying that -
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗？听上去就是这个意思啊\NReally? That sounds like what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.17,0:39:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来就是你被图雷特氏症打倒了\NIt sounds like you're letting Tourette's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.44,0:39:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没让图雷特氏症打倒我\NI am not letting Tourette's win!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.47,0:39:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗？ - 对！\N-Really?   -Yes, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.71,0:39:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不会放弃，我只是…\NLook, I'm never going to give up, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.38,0:39:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找对学校才行\NI have to find the right school.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.41,0:39:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你会的，波波，你会的\NYou will, Bobo. You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.02,0:39:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的结论是：此事无关图雷特氏症\NSo, I decided it wasn't Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.32,0:39:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是还没找到合适的学校\NI just hadn't found the right school yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.76,0:39:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要继续找，不找到好校长是不会放弃的\NI'd keep barking, and I wasn't quitting until I found that principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.70,0:39:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我在地图上标出了每一所我还没面试过的学校\NI made a map of every school where I hadn't interviewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.86,0:40:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果校长不在，我就把履历给秘书或管理员\Nlf the Principal wasn't in, I'd give my resume to a secretary or a janitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.80,0:40:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,请他们等校长回来后拿给他看\Nand ask them to drop it off when the principal returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.47,0:40:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎，我需要一份工作\NI didn't care. I needed a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.48,0:40:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我没找到工作就不轻言罢休\NI wasn't going to stop until I had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.02,0:40:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你得从基层做起\NYou'll be starting at the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.95,0:40:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样很正常，我也是白手起家\Nbut that's no big deal, that's where I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.89,0:40:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你上班时间是7点到4点\NAnd you're working 7 to 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.39,0:40:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过这是兼职性质的\NI told you this is only part time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.69,0:40:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我早上要面试，不能来上班\NI need to keep mornings open for interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.93,0:40:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,学校不是早就开学了吗？\NI thought that school had already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有些学校还没有\NNo, not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.90,0:40:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,再看情况吧\NWell, we'll see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.93,0:40:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的干活工具，至少暂时的啦\NHere are your tools of the trade - at least for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.50,0:40:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了，要从基层做起\NLike I said, at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.04,0:40:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里的每份工作都很重要，天晓得\NBut every job is important here,and - who knows -
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.24,0:40:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你做一做会爱上，只要你投入时间…\Nmaybe you'll end up liking it. And if you put your time in...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.61,0:40:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我刚才讲的你没听见吗？\NDidn't you hear what I just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.98,0:40:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只在这里上班到我找到教职\NI'm only working here until I get a teaching job --
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.62,0:41:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那些东西都要搬去垃圾堆\NAll that stuff has to go in the dumpster.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.99,0:41:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,聘任教师的季节快结束了\NThe hiring season was ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.06,0:41:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的面试机会没了，学校已经开学\NMy interviews had dried up. School had started.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.73,0:41:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我没时间，也没钱…和希望\NI was running out of time and money...and hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.17,0:41:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,黛安\NDiane.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.47,0:41:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不指望你会来找我了，所以我直接来找你\NI gave up on you ever coming to me, so I just came to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.05,0:41:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你在忙吗？\NYou busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.85,0:41:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的继母黛安，她想用咸面包来拉拢我\NIt was my stepmom, Diane. Trying to build bridges with bagels.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.28,0:41:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸是凭双手打造他的事业\NYour Dad built his business with his own two hands;
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.59,0:41:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他希望你能参与，你不能怪他\Nyou can't blame him for wanting you to be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.72,0:41:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是尽力在作一个父亲的本分\NHe's just being a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.39,0:41:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他希望你能融入他的生活\NHe wants you in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.23,0:41:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢亚特兰大吗？有没有认识好女孩？\NSo how do you like Atlanta? You meet any nice girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.77,0:41:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我讲话都讲不到重点，对吧？\NI'm just saying all the right things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.91,0:42:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我再帮你倒一杯\NLet me get you a refill --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.31,0:42:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德…\NBrad. Brad,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.38,0:42:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸很爱你\Nyour dad loves you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.82,0:42:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,非常爱你\N...so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.82,0:42:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是不想看到你受伤\NHe just doesn't want to see you get hurt -
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.56,0:42:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上最让我受伤的是：他从来就不接受真正的我\NThe only thing that hurts is the fact that he has never accepted who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.13,0:42:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他脑海里有个完美儿子的形象\NSee, he's got this idea of a perfect son,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.66,0:42:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人很正常，做的都是正常的事\Nwho is "normal" and does "normal" things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.80,0:42:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而我永远也不可能达到那种“正常”\NWell, I'm never gonna be "normal"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.20,0:42:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这些不是他想法，布莱德\NWell, maybe that's not his idea, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.90,0:42:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而只是你的想法。你说得对，你是不正常\NMaybe that's yours. And you're right, you are not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.51,0:42:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你有教学的天分\NYou have this gift to teach,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.95,0:42:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些天分不是来自你的图雷特氏症\Nand it's not in spite of your Tourette's,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.72,0:42:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为它本来就有\Nit's because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.17,0:42:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了\NI have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.40,0:43:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,(现在球传到三垒，再传到一垒， 目前是一好一坏)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.47,0:43:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(准备投球，外侧过低的滑球)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.27,0:43:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(两好一坏)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.32,0:43:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，我是布莱德\NHello, this is Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.49,0:43:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，是的\NAhh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.20,0:43:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我养了牧羊犬\NThat's a sheepdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.00,0:43:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对，布莱德，布莱德·科恩\NYep, Brad. Brad Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.70,0:43:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,十点，我没问题\NTen o'clock is - is perfect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.80,0:43:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好，好极了\NAbsolutely. OK, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.51,0:43:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,(山景小学)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.51,0:43:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,（举手，举手！）\NRaise your hand. Raise your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.55,0:43:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（你们要先举手，来！）\NYou gotta raise your hand! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.05,0:44:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是布莱德·科恩吧\NYou must be Brad Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.12,0:44:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨！\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.96,0:44:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是吉姆·欧贝，本校的校长\NI'm Jim Ovbey; I'm the Principal around here. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.56,0:44:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉里·史崔卡，副校长\NHilarie Straka, Assistant Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.49,0:44:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.00,0:44:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,进办公室聊，布莱德\NCome on in the office, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.60,0:44:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你大老远从停车场过来\NWe heard you coming all the way from the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.13,0:44:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你每间学校都跑遍了\NHear you've been making the rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.30,0:44:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,目前为止是25间，这是我的履历表\NTwenty-five schools so far. And, uh, here's, here's my resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.00,0:44:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我吧\N-Oh. Here. -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.84,0:44:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们待会儿再看，布莱德\NWe can look at that in a minute, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.37,0:44:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,先进来，谈谈你为什么想当老师\NJust come on in,tell us why you want to be a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.14,0:44:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.31,0:44:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，这个，这是我毕生最大的愿望\NWell, it's, uh,oh, it's, it's all I ever wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.25,0:44:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,从我还在念书到现在\NEver since I was in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.89,0:44:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有什么好老师激励了你\NYou must have had some pretty inspiring teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.25,0:44:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是有位校长激励了我，麦尔先生\NAh, well. I had an inspiring principal -- Mr. Myer -
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.49,0:44:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的老师们，他们\Nbut my teachers, they really only
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.43,0:44:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,给我的启发都只是让我别像他们一样\Ninspired me to be the kind of teachers they never were.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.06,0:44:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要当怎样的老师？\NWhat kind of teacher is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.97,0:44:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,即使有一个学生与众不同，也要给他学习的机会\NOne who makes it possible for a kid to learn even if he's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.84,0:45:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我最好的老师应该算是图雷特氏症吧\NIn a way, the, the best teacher I ever had was my Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布莱德，你可以不必谈这个\NYou, you don't have to talk about that, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.88,0:45:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没关系，我早就下定决心要直言不讳了\NNo, it's OK. I make a point of being open about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.38,0:45:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不给学生们设限\NIt's, ah, never off-limits to my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.92,0:45:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们随时可以问我任何问题\NThey can ask me anything they want about it at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.99,0:45:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有些问题想必很有趣吧\NYou must get some pretty interesting questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.56,0:45:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对，有时候会牵涉到隐私\NOh, yeah. Sometimes it gets really personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.99,0:45:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,希望这个问题对你不会太隐私\NI hope this question isn't too personal, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.77,0:45:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡觉时会不会发出怪声？\NDo you make those noises in your sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.37,0:45:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，我睡着了啊\NI don't know. I'm asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.51,0:45:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦，我睡觉时不会发出怪声\NNo. No, I don't tic in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.78,0:45:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我放松时就不会发出怪声了，比如现在\NWhen I'm relaxed, the noises give me a little bit of a break. Like just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.08,0:45:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我想多了解你的教学理念\NOkay Brad. I want to hear more about your teaching philosophy...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.32,0:45:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我很乐意分享我的教学理念\NYeah. I'd love to tell you about my teaching philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.22,0:45:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊了将近两个小时，这是我最棒的一次面试经验\NWe talked for nearly two hours, it was the best interview I'd ever had -
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.66,0:45:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布莱德，很高兴认识你\NWell, Brad, it was a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.93,0:46:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也是\NYou, too. You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.27,0:46:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要再面试几位老师\NWe've still got a few more teachers to interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.50,0:46:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦决定好就会通知你\NBut we'll let you know when we've made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.37,0:46:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好，太好了\NOk, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.57,0:46:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢     - 谢谢两位\N-Thank you. -Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.45,0:46:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我这多年的伙伴还是一样，警告我不要抱太大的失望\NStill, my Constant Companion, as always, warned me not to get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.79,0:46:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但希望是很难戒掉的习惯\NBut hope is a hard habit to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.24,0:47:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后一次被找去和二年级的教职员面谈\NI was called one last time to and asked come in and meet with the second grade staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.34,0:47:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你教过二年级？\NOh, so, you student-taught second grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.01,0:47:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我超爱二年级，那些小孩都像海绵一样\NOh, I love second grade! The kids are still so open-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.08,0:47:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不管教他们什么都可以吸收\NThey're open to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.42,0:47:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对，但还是要维持一点纪律吧？\NYes, but you do manage to maintain a little discipline, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.26,0:47:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让他们什么都吸收啊\NWhile they're being so open?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.82,0:47:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我会让他们知道分寸的\NI do let them know what the boundaries are. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.26,0:47:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，你认为你必须要教的，最重要的是什么？\NSo, Brad. What do you think is the most important thing you have to teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.76,0:47:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯……\NYeah. Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.10,0:47:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,除了识字的重要性和数学的价值以外\NBesides the importance of reading and the value of math...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.30,0:47:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要教他们接纳自己\Nthat it's okay to be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.37,0:47:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,色彩涂到线框外也没关系，反正你就是这样的人\NIt's okay to color outside the lines if that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.91,0:47:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就可以忽略界线吗？\NSo it's okay to ignore the boundaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.45,0:47:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，我没有…\NNo, and I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.32,0:47:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉，但你一直这么做下去\NI'm sorry but how can you expect kids to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.09,0:47:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得学生怎么还能学习？\Nwhen you're doing that all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.42,0:47:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托，布兰妲…\NOh. Come on, Brenda --
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.86,0:47:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不，不，没关系，这个问题很好\NNo, no, no. It's OK. It's a valid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.33,0:47:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意回答\NI want to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.20,0:48:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,学生在了解我之前，有时候会觉得我很怪，甚至可怕\NBefore they know me, kids sometimes do think I'm just weird, even scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.13,0:48:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但等我跟他们解释了图雷特氏症\NBut, once I educate them about my Tourette's --
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.14,0:48:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会知道科恩老师是个普通人\Nand they see that Mr. Cohen is a real person
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.41,0:48:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只是碰巧会发出一些怪声\Nwho just happens to make funny noises,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.61,0:48:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们就认同我是个好老师\Nwell, then they accept me as a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.21,0:48:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就像他们接受你们在座各位一样\NJust like they accept all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.45,0:48:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该向二年级的学生多学学\NWell, maybe we should all try to be more like second-graders.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.72,0:48:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还有谁有问题要问科恩先生？\NDoes anyone have any other questions for Mr. Cohen?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.26,0:48:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，谢谢你抽空过来\NBrad thanks for coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.56,0:48:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,校方会跟你联络，请你耐心等\NThe school will be in touch with you, so just be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.40,0:48:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,当你感觉到最后一次机会也搞砸了，要耐心等真的很难\NIt's hard to be patient when you feel as though you've blown your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.87,0:48:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且耐心从来就不是我这个多年伙伴的强项\NAnd patience never was my Constant Companion's strong suit --
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.54,0:48:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那所学校应该没跟你联络吧\NI'm guessing you never heard from that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.84,0:48:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有，他们还在面试\NNo, not yet. They're still interviewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.21,0:48:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不担心\NI'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.35,0:48:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.61,0:48:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思？\NIs that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.98,0:48:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说“好吧”\NI just said "okay".
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.75,0:48:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的意思\NI know what you mean
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.99,0:48:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想：只有别人还有选择，就不会选中我\Nyou don't think anybody would hire me if they had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.95,0:48:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是干什么？读心术吗？\NWhat are you, a mind-reader now?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.76,0:49:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，今天是我最后一天上班\NYou know what, Dad? This is gonna be my last day here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.69,0:49:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不等找到工作再说？\NWell, why don't you wait and see if you got the job first?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.93,0:49:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会找到工作的\NI'm gonna get the job, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.16,0:49:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我要保持专注\NI just have to stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.40,0:49:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道不能同时专注和实际吗？\NWhy can't you stay focused and realistic at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.73,0:49:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样有什么不好？\NWhat's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.64,0:49:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去吧\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.58,0:49:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？你这样会受伤啦\NWhoa! Are you all right, man? You'll knock yourself out doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.35,0:49:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你开车时这样怎么办？\NWhat if that happens while you're driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.95,0:49:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.75,0:49:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对啦，我不知道，你应该换个医生看看\NUh, yeah, I don't know. You oughta see another doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.12,0:49:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都在看医生，根本没用\NI've seen doctors my whole life, Ron. OK? They don't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.32,0:49:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得要找个人看看吗？\NWell, don't you think you need to see somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.09,0:49:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不需要\NI really don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.20,0:49:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你就…\NSo, just.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.47,0:49:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.38,0:49:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我又在等电话响了\NWaiting for the phone to ring again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.58,0:49:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说服自己，有好事会发生\NI tried to convince myself something good would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.36,0:50:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是我弟弟，我没想到他会来\NMy kid brother...not exactly what I had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.13,0:50:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好啊，波波      - 杰夫！\N- How are you doing, Bobo?  -Jeff,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.16,0:50:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会来？怎么没事先告诉我？\Nwhat, what are you doing here? Why didn't you tell me you were coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.74,0:50:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上穿的是短裤耶\NYou know you're in your boxers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.77,0:50:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是老妈叫你来查我的勤吗？\NDid, ah, Mom send you to check up on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.37,0:50:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛？你需要别人查勤？\NWhy? You need checking up on?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.28,0:50:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦，就…\NNo, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.84,0:50:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的东西要放哪儿？\NWhere do I put my stuff?.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.48,0:50:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很好，你睡沙发\NThat's great. You get the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.11,0:50:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这高尔夫球杆不错，新的吗？\NWhoa! Nice clubs, are these new?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.72,0:50:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都是老爸的，他借我用\NAh. They're Dad's, he let me borrow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.39,0:50:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找你去打打高尔夫球\NThought maybe you and I could, ah, play a little golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.59,0:50:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我们去他那个俱乐部打\NHe got us a tee-time at his club.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.69,0:50:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎样？这里要用3号铁杆？\NSo, what do you think? Three iron from here, little bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.06,0:50:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，谢谢你带我来打球\NHey, by the way,thanks for the round.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.23,0:50:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢老爸吧，等一下…\NThank Dad. Oh, wait, forgot....
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.60,0:50:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了你们不讲话\N...you guys aren't speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.27,0:50:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不想提到老爸\NI don't want to talk about Dad right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.10,0:50:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样讲只是想激我啦\NYou're just saying that to rattle me because you know -
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.07,0:50:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会赢你\NI'm going to beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.01,0:50:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真的，你跟爸该和好了啦\NI'm serious, Brad, you and Dad gotta start getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.98,0:51:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们处得很好啊\NWe get along fine -
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.74,0:51:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只要保持够远的距离就好了\Nas long as we keep it long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.31,0:51:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才搬来这里吗？为了保持够远的距离？\NIs that why you moved down here? To keep it long distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.28,0:51:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你没什么好向他证明的吧？\NI mean, it's not like you have anything to prove to him -- right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.12,0:51:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎样？你改当心理医生了？杰夫医生？\NWhat are you now, Jeff, a shrink? Dr. Jeff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.99,0:51:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\NI'm sorry, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.06,0:51:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请你别再发出那种怪声\NI'm going to have to ask you to stop making those noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.79,0:51:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老兄\NLook, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.26,0:51:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是故意的，他有…     - 没关系，我自己来就好了\N-He's not doing it on purpose, he's got-  -No, no, no. I can handle it, Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.49,0:51:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了\NI got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.30,0:51:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这样对其他要打球的人不公平\NLook, it's just not fair to the other golfers.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.93,0:51:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我懂，只是我不能控制不发出怪声\NNo, I understand, that, umm, I can't help making these noises
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.47,0:51:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我有图雷特氏症\Nbecause I have Tourette Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.83,0:51:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种神经性疾病，我来解释给你听\NIt's a neurological disorder; I'd like to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.24,0:51:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你应该离开这个球场\NYou're gonna have to leave the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.47,0:51:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要替其他会员着想\NI gotta think of the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.04,0:51:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,乔，别为难他了，他没怎么的\NHey, Joe. Leave the guy alone. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.65,0:51:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，老兄，我们俩来搭档吧，我约好的朋友没来\NHey, man. We're a twosome and our buddies don't appear to be showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.88,0:51:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要跟我们一起？\NWould you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.82,0:51:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你还不走，我就要叫保安了\Nlf you don't leave, I'm going to have to call security.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.45,0:51:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的，好的      - 你…\N-OK, OK. Umm...   -You...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.22,0:51:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们，明年再来吧，好吗？\NOK. Thanks, guys. Maybe next year, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.09,0:51:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,杰夫，我们走。 走了，老兄，谢谢\NJeff, come on. Come on, buddy. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.10,0:52:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，杰夫？这种场面你又不是没见过\NCome on, Jeff, it's not like you haven't seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.00,0:52:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都这么无知，你怎么受得了生活在这种世界？\NHow can you stand living in a world where everybody's so ignorant?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.14,0:52:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是每个人都这样，你也看到刚才那两个打球的人\NEverybody's not. You saw those golfers back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.74,0:52:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还帮我讲话，我的人生中到处都有那样的人\NThey went to bat for me.My life is full of people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.01,0:52:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我就很少遇到好人了\NThat's not always been my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.18,0:52:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为你老是为了挺我而打架\NWell, that's because you're always getting into fights sticking up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.25,0:52:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你和妈都是，你们老是在维护我\NYou and mom. You've always been there for me and my tics.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.19,0:52:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道吗？我开始觉得你很烦了。比赛看谁先到车上\NYou know what? You're beginning to"tick" me off... race you to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.76,0:52:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？     - 笨蛋！\N-Oh, yeah? What! Hey! HEY! - Sucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.32,0:52:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,杰夫的来访让我暂时忘却烦恼，你作弊！\NJeff's visit did give me a break from my worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.83,0:52:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在他走后，我就接到学校的来电\NAnd, right after he left,I got a call from the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.13,0:52:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,校长要我去见他\NThe principal wanted to see me in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.14,0:52:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跟小时候一样\NJust like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.25,0:52:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,挺吵的吧？\NPretty noisy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.19,0:52:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但小朋友们都能接受，不是吗？\NAnd yet somehow the kids manage, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.46,0:53:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，他们都能接受\NYes, they do. They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.93,0:53:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉里和我跟老师们讨论过你的情况\NHilarie and I discussed you with the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.64,0:53:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊到自己有多骄傲能教给孩子们\NAnd, we talked about how proud we are of teaching our kids
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.64,0:53:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不让任何事拦住他们的人生前路\Nto never let anything hold them back in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.41,0:53:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉里说如果我们要想说得漂亮\NAnd, Hilarie said that if we're gonna talk the talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.35,0:53:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就得做得漂亮\Nwe need to walk the walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.82,0:53:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她在等着带你去参观教室\NShe's waiting to show you your classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.06,0:53:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你\NWelcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.20,0:53:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,二年级人很多，所以要多开一班\NSecond grade is overcrowded so we've had to create a new class.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.73,0:53:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的学生都是从别班调来的\NYour kids are being taken out of other rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.83,0:53:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有几个还搞不清楚状况\Nso some of them might be a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.34,0:53:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已进来这间学校三个礼拜了\NThey've already been in school for three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.21,0:53:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的学生名单在那里\NThere's your student roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.88,0:53:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,礼拜一就开始上课\NThe fun starts Monday, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.22,0:53:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么需要尽管告诉我\NLet me know if there's anything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.69,0:53:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都需要\NI need everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.36,0:54:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我低头看着那份学生名单\NI looked down at that roster like I was announcing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.62,0:54:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像在宣布，明星棒球队的先发球员名单\Nthe starting line-up for an all star baseball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.99,0:54:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 希拉里，这是…谢谢你…\NHilarie, this is, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.56,0:54:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们想说你可能会需要这些\NHey! We thought you might need these.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.10,0:54:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，都搬进来吧\NHey, everybody, bring them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.64,0:54:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,先随便放，放好再来整理\NJust put them down anywhere. We'll get them arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.64,0:54:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给我，我来帮忙，谢谢\NHere, let me help you with that.Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.25,0:54:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来山景小学\NWelcome to Mountain View.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.42,0:54:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对，妈，这真是太好了\NYeah, Mom, it's phenomenal, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.09,0:54:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但我好不容易才等到这一天\Nit's taken me so long to get here I still have to remind myself
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.49,0:54:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我还得提醒自己一切才刚开始\Nthat I'm just at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.32,0:54:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝，这是个天大的好消息！太好了\NHoney, that is, that is wonderful news! That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.53,0:54:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，妈妈\NYes, yes, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.10,0:54:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这的确非常好，但是 -\NIt is absolutely wonderful, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.63,0:54:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只跟我签约一年\Nthey've only given me a contract for a year. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.97,0:54:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还得向他们证明他们没看错人\NI still have to prove to them that they made the right choice --
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.77,0:54:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 宝贝，你先享受这一刻吧\NHoney, listen, just take a moment to enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.21,0:54:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪，我…\NOh my gosh. Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.54,0:54:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有跟你爸讲？他一定会很骄傲的\NDid you call your father? He is gonna be so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.28,0:54:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉他的，妈妈，但现在\NI will, Mom. But, you know, right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.04,0:54:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我得在两天之内准备好两个礼拜要做完的事\NI literally have about two weeks of preparation to do in about two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.65,0:55:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我找到工作了\NAnd, ah, you know, now that I have the job,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.45,0:55:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要认真开始进修硕士学位\NI gotta really seriously start working on getting my Master's degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.65,0:55:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦，一次做一件事\NOK, one thing at a time, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.96,0:55:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,学校里有没有漂亮的女老师？\NListen. Are there any cute teachers at that school?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.06,0:55:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈！\NMom!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.63,0:55:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么嘛？我只是希望你快乐啊\NWhat? I want you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.23,0:55:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦\NOK, all right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.56,0:55:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧，我在用心了。先这样了，再见\NDon't worry; I'm working on that, too. I gotta go. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.35,0:55:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(婚友联谊网)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.45,0:55:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你是布莱德吧\NYou must be Brad....
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.49,0:55:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是南茜吧\NYou must be Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.66,0:55:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，我是布莱德\NHi, I'm Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.99,0:55:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.46,0:55:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我只是有点紧张\NRight. Of course. I guess I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.50,0:55:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.73,0:55:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次和网友约会\NThis is my first time computer dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.70,0:55:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…   - 对\N-So...  - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.80,0:55:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我也是，我妈觉得这很危险\NMe too. My mom thinks it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.54,0:55:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，谁知道你会遇到什么怪人\NWell, yeah, I mean, you never know what kind of weirdo you might meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.04,0:56:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但你看起来蛮正常的\NBut you look pretty normal. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.81,0:56:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好，我真高兴\NGood, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.85,0:56:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你比正常更好啦\NActually, look much better than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.42,0:56:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.25,0:56:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我觉得我们应该介绍下自己的情况吧\NSo, ahh, I guess we're just supposed to tell each other our life stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.39,0:56:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\NUmm, OK. Do, do...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.80,0:56:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那我能不能先来杯咖啡？\N...you think I could get a, get a cup of coffee first?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.93,0:56:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咖啡？    - 对\N-Cup of coffee. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.57,0:56:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好，没问题，马上来\NRight. Yeah! Of course. Coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.77,0:56:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.44,0:56:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要来个松饼蛋糕？\NAh. Do you want, like, a muffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.57,0:56:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我在节食\NI'm on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.07,0:56:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但我好想吃松饼蛋糕\NBut I would love a muffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.82,0:56:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我室友快把我搞疯了\NMy roommate is driving me absolutely crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.89,0:56:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她从来不整理床铺，衣服到处丢\NShe never makes her bed;she's got clothes everywhere;
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.19,0:56:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她从早到晚都在大声听音乐\Nshe's, like, always blasting her music...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.00,0:56:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但我每次听我的音乐\N...night and day. But, of course, whenever I want to listen to my music,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.20,0:56:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她就说“你得放小声一点”\Nshe's all, like, "you need to keep it down".
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.07,0:57:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你都听什么音乐？\NSo what kind of music do you listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.90,0:57:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就…嗯     - 什么？\N-Well, umm,  -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.91,0:57:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分都是老歌啦，尤其是史汀…\NMostly oldies stuff. Especially Sting -
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.08,0:57:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我超爱史汀的\NOh, I love Sting!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.41,0:57:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 麦当娜、邦·乔维\NMadonna, Bon Jovi, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.38,0:57:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 米利·维尼里？\NMilli Vanilli...?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.29,0:57:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢米利·维尼里\NI love Milli Vanilli!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.99,0:57:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.12,0:57:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，你也喜欢？\NWait. You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.12,0:57:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界大概只有我们两个人\NWe've gotta be the only two people on earth -
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.39,0:57:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢米利·维尼里吧\Nthat love Milli Vanilli.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.06,0:57:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不会吧\NYou do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.76,0:57:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.50,0:57:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天好开心，谢谢你\NWell, I had a really nice time. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.34,0:57:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该吃那个松饼蛋糕啦\NI shouldn't have had that muffin but...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.84,0:57:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我很高兴能认识你\NI really enjoyed meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.14,0:57:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也是\NYeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.82,0:57:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，谢谢你，布莱德\NOK. Well, thanks again, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.77,0:58:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真搞不懂你！你说她很完美\NI can't believe you! You said she was perfect --
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.57,0:58:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她是很完美啊。我只是不想毁了这一切\NShe was perfect. I just didn't want to ruin it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.77,0:58:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再约她见面会毁了一切？哦，对啦：再约会综合症\NOh, by asking to see her again? Oh, right: second date syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.31,0:58:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那你打算就这样过一生？第一次约会就结束？\NSo is that gonna be your life? Nothing but first and only dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.25,0:58:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你怎么可能有进一步的发展？\NHow do you ever expect to have a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.92,0:58:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也许就不要有啊\NMaybe I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.02,0:58:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(新邮件)
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.02,0:58:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(南茜：我在听米利·维里尼，想到认识同好的你有多幸运)
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.02,0:58:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(布莱德：我也是)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.48,0:59:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,(欢迎来上科恩老师的课)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.82,0:59:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(科恩老师)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.03,0:59:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,(不一样也没关系)
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.25,1:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请进，进来吧，请进\NCome on in. Get in there. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.20,1:00:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怪胎！\NWeirdo!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.98,1:00:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,(图雷特氏综合症)
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.28,1:00:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的老师有警告过，科恩老师会发出怪声吗？\NDid your teachers warn you that Mr. Cohen makes funny noises?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.05,1:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有\NYeeesss.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.52,1:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她说你有图…图…\NShe said you have Tour...tour...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.99,1:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 图雷特氏症\NTourette Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.02,1:00:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好，想知道什么就问吧\NOK. Anything you want to know about it,I want you to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.33,1:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.10,1:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会传染？\NIs it catching...?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.66,1:00:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不会，绝对不会\NNo. Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.87,1:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是天生的，像我一样\NYou have to be born with it,like I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.64,1:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会痛？\NDoes it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.00,1:00:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候，比如颈部抽搐就会痛\NWell, sometimes,like when my neck jerks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.31,1:00:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但发出怪声不会痛啦\NBut the noises do not hurt at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.14,1:00:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,问得很好，继续问\NThese are great questions,keep 'em coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.71,1:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,关于图雷特氏症的事都可以问我\NAnd, it's okay to ask me anything -about Tourette's
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.11,1:00:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,请说\N- yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.92,1:00:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可以去看电影吗？\NCan you go to movies?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.38,1:00:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我可以去看电影\NYes, I can go to movies,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.62,1:00:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时候会被赶出来，这让我觉得很难过\Nbut sometimes I get kicked out and that makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.42,1:01:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那只兔子叫什么名字？\NWhat's the bunny's name?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.26,1:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,威…威…威化\NWaffle --
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.36,1:01:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,威 威 威化\NWa Wa Waffle!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.07,1:01:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它名字只是威化啦\NHis name is just Waffle!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.07,1:01:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NAll right, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.00,1:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还有关于图雷特氏症的疑问吗？\NAny more questions about Tourette's?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.28,1:01:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有？\NAnyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.01,1:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师，你能不能好起来？\NAre they ever gonna make you well, Mr. Cohen?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.88,1:01:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,目前是没有药可以治好图雷特氏症\NWell. Right now there's no medicine that can cure Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.95,1:01:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但没关系\NBut, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.92,1:01:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我学会了接受，我不会让它毁了我的一生\NCuz I've learned to accept it and I don't let it run my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.79,1:01:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么不能做的吗？比如不能吃东西？\NWhat can't you do? Like...can you not eat?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.89,1:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吃东西，而且我很会吃哦\NI can eat. OK, I eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.73,1:01:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,其实别人能做的事我都能做\NIn fact, I can do anything anybody else can do except
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.10,1:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师只有一件事不能做\Nthere is one thing that Mr. Cohen can never do.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.50,1:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？  - 不，我不能说\NWhat?     - No. I can't
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.74,1:01:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是什么？     - 不，我不能说\NWhat is it?    - No. I can't
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.47,1:01:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉我们嘛\N- Tell us
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.51,1:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师永远不能玩\NMr. Cohen can never play -
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.48,1:01:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,捉迷藏\Nhide and go seek.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.78,1:02:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么你不能玩捉迷藏？\NWhy can't you play hide and seek?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.25,1:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因为会被人听到啦，笨蛋\NCause they'd hear him, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.52,1:02:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,答对了，但用这样的字眼是不对的\NWell, that's the right answer but it's the wrong words
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.76,1:02:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在科恩老师班上不能骂人\Nbecause there won't be any name- calling in Mr. Cohen's class,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.43,1:02:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好，请问你要去哪儿？\NExcuse me? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.73,1:02:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 上厕所\NBathroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.60,1:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么名字？\NAnd what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.50,1:02:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 托马斯\NThomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.46,1:02:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好，托马斯，如果你要离开座位\NOK. Well, Thomas,if you want to leave your seat,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.60,1:02:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就要先征求我的同意\Nyou have to ask for permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.87,1:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怪胎\NWeirdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.84,1:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 科恩老师再见\NBye, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.64,1:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 盖伦再见\NBye, Gaylon.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.78,1:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师再见\NGood bye, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.21,1:02:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,再见，海瑟，明天见\NBye Heather, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.02,1:02:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢上你的课，科恩老师\NI really like your class, Mr. Cohen!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.82,1:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，阿曼达  - 莱特先生，你好吗？\NOh, well, thank you, Amanda! How are you doing Mr. Wright?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.26,1:02:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我很好\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.23,1:02:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,四眼田鸡！\NFour eyes!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.70,1:02:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 四眼田鸡\NFour eyes!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.33,1:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 口香糖给我   - 不要过来！\N-Gimme gum!   -Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.13,1:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，你抓住他，托马斯\NOK, take him, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.93,1:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱！托马斯！你们谁想帮我？\NEli! Thomas! Which one of you guys thinks that you can help me? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.67,1:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我要！我要！\NI can, I can!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.30,1:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好，这样吧\NAll right, all right. Here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.24,1:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个球要放回篮子里\NI need to get this ball and put it back in that bin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.04,1:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来猜拳决定\NWhy don't you guys shoot for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.54,1:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀、石头、布\NRock, paper, scissor, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.24,1:03:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好，伊莱，你今天赢了\NWhoa! All right, Eli. You win today. Boom!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.78,1:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哎哟！\NAh, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.51,1:03:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没关系啦，托马斯，你去帮他\NIt's OK, Thomas, you can help him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.89,1:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我把托马斯丢给了你  但他实在闹得我不能上课\NSorry I stuck you with Thomas,but he was making my class impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.63,1:03:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他有一大堆问题：注意力缺陷症、过动症\NHe's got a whole alphabet of problems:ADD, ADHD, OCD.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.97,1:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的劝，把他转去特教班吧\NYou want my advice,you'll pass him on to Special Ed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.40,1:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.21,1:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这么做\NI can't, ah, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.81,1:03:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等他妨碍你几堂课你就知道了\NOh. See how you feel after he's trashed a few classes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.48,1:03:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的啦  我只需要适应一下\NI'll be all right.I just need to get settled.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.95,1:03:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我等不及明天了\NI can't wait for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.65,1:03:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.67,1:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我的喇叭还要吵啦\NYou make more noise than my air horn.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.97,1:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像是有图雷特氏症吧\NSounds like you got healthy case of Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.57,1:04:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的啦，我有个同事也有图雷特氏症\NI was just kidding with you, son. I've got a dispatcher buddy with TS.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.68,1:04:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你有要搬的东西就找玛克辛吧\NYou ever need any cross-country hauling, just call for Maxine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.05,1:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你有名片吗？\NHey, umm. Do you have a card?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.82,1:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是认真的啦，小子，除非你是从事运输业\NI wasn't being serious, son. Unless you're in the shipping business.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.89,1:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，我是二年级的老师\NNah, I teach second grade.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.16,1:04:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(玛克辛的红卡车)
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.29,1:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我的名片     - 好\N-Here's the card.  - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.29,1:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,玛克辛给了我一个地理课的好主意\NMaxine gave me a great idea for a geography lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.00,1:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，玛克辛\NThank you so much, Maxine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.70,1:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不客气\NYou're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.13,1:04:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小心开车\NSafe trucking.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.04,1:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现自己的关注点都放在教书上了\NI found myself focusing on teaching all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.14,1:04:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎啦\NWell, almost...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.64,1:05:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道我刚才发现什么？\NYou know what I just realized?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.88,1:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.05,1:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的鸭子都有图雷特氏症\NAll ducks have Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.22,1:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\NWhy is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.02,1:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，我跟它们是同类\NI don't know.We're birds of a feather.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.50,1:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你一点也不介意吧？\NSo, it really doesn't bother you,does it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.54,1:05:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.27,1:05:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你明知故问，我的图雷特氏症啊，我发出的怪声\NYou know what. My Tourette's... my noises.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.68,1:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,跟别的男人比起来就没什么啦\NNot when I compare them to the noises other guys make.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.82,1:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是吹牛、讲话超大声、自我中心、一堆自大的白痴\NYou know, like, braggers, loud-talkers, egocentric, humor-challenged idiots.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.36,1:06:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不会，你的怪声我毫不介意\NSeriously, no.Your noises don't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.69,1:06:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你一直逗我笑就好了\NAs long as you keep me laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.10,1:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样讲，你知道我压力大会怎样\NWell, don't say that.You know how I get under pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.73,1:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NOh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.80,1:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸早就知道我会嫁给逗我笑的人\NMy Dad has always said I was going to marry somebody who made me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.07,1:06:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我这样讲没什么特别的用意\NNot that that has anything to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.75,1:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,讲话嘛\NSay something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.13,1:06:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,呱！\NQuack.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.79,1:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别笑，我呱得很认真\NHey. Don't laugh.That was a serious quack.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.60,1:06:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我有吓到你喔\NI got you though.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.27,1:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 科恩老师\NMr. Cohen!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.71,1:06:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.68,1:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈要我问你可不可以\NMy Mom said to ask if it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.91,1:06:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么可不可以，海瑟？\NIs what okay, Heather?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.41,1:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这个可不可以给威化吃\Nlf I give this to Waffle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.08,1:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你妈妈我说可以\NYou tell your Mom that I said that's fine. OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.66,1:07:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他说可以吗？\NDid he say it was OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.56,1:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.69,1:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好吗？\NFeel OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.53,1:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NUm-Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.03,1:07:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是喔，我爱你\NYeah? I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.33,1:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也爱你\NI love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.13,1:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你今天要乖哦\NYou have a good day, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.20,1:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好\NOK!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.00,1:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我放学再来接你\NI'll see you right after school.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.10,1:07:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好，再见\NOK. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.58,1:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达？你还好吧？\NAmanda? Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.48,1:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想上你的课，科恩老师\NI wanna be in your class, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.12,1:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就在我班上啊，阿曼达\NYou are in my class, Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.19,1:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没了，他叫学校把我转到别班\NNo. He made them take me out --
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.76,1:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我放学后再来接你\NSee you after school, honey. OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.73,1:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平！\NIt's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.50,1:07:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？我是阿曼达的老师科恩\NIs everything OK? I'm Amanda's teacher, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.80,1:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们昨天见过\N-We met yesterday. -Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.67,1:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，没什么问题啦\NThere's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.14,1:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是要为我女儿着想\NI just have to do what's right for my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.67,1:07:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，阿曼达\NCome on, Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.14,1:07:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,走了啦\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.44,1:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他担心阿曼达不能专心\NHe's concerned about Amanda's ability to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.52,1:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得你是她学习上的阻碍\NHe just thought that you'd make it a little harder for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.15,1:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能给我一次机会吗？\NCan't he just give me a chance?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.09,1:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,学期才刚开始\NWe've only just started.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.52,1:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有讲了\NI pointed that out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.79,1:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后呢？\NAnd?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.19,1:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他很同情\NHe said he was sympathetic
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.69,1:08:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但他说阿曼达需要正常的老师\Nbut that Amanda needs -- as he put it -a "normal teacher."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.96,1:08:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，你别放在心上，家长是老师最难解的课题\NDon't take it to heart, Brad. Parents are the hardest part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.67,1:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好，有谁知道玛克辛和她的大红卡车\NAll right, who can tell me the names of the capitals Maxine
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.24,1:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要经过哪几州的首府？ 有谁知道？\Nand her big red truck have passed through? Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.08,1:08:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思…天哪，\NOh, all these hands! Excuse me. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.28,1:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我该选谁？\NAh, man. Who do I choose?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.32,1:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道耶\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.79,1:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,海瑟\NHeather.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.25,1:08:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,亚特兰大、纳什维尔、斯普林菲尔德\NAtlanta...Nashville...um... Springfield?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.93,1:08:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,答对了，很多人都以为是芝加哥\NThat's great! Because a lot of people think it's Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.43,1:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林菲尔德是在这儿吧？\NAnd, ah, this is Springfield, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.53,1:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不对！\NNoooo.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.33,1:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是印地安纳波利斯\NThat's Indianapolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.93,1:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,答对了\NOh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.04,1:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想什么啊  这才是斯普林菲尔德\NSo, what am I thinking? This is Springfield.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.80,1:09:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不对！\NNO!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.17,1:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是哥伦布，斯普林菲尔德在这里，科恩老师\NThat's Columbus! Springfield's over there, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.14,1:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里，伊莱？是在这里吗？\NWhere is it, Eli? Is it over here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.85,1:09:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是！\NNooo!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.38,1:09:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林菲尔德在哪里？\NWhere is Springfield?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.05,1:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，你们要指给我看\NI don't know.You guys have to point it out to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.02,1:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,指给我看…\NPoint it out. Point it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.29,1:09:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不到啊\NI don't see it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.13,1:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了\NAhh! I see it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.93,1:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是说这才是斯普林菲尔德吧？\NYou're telling me that this is Springfield. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.63,1:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对！\NYES!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.10,1:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我没同意你离开座位，托马斯\NYou don't have permission to leave your seat, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.20,1:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对，科恩老师的后脑勺有长眼睛\NThat's right. Mr. Cohen has eyes in the back of his head.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.30,1:09:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,请你回去坐好  下次要先问我\NGo back and sit down, please.And next time, ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.54,1:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要削铅笔啊\NBut I need to sharpen my pencil.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.18,1:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回来坐好，托马斯\NNow, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.42,1:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NAll right, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.55,1:09:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,玛克辛和她的大红卡车礼拜二要去哪里？\NWhere's Maxine and her bug red truck going to be on Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.75,1:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我！我！\NME! ME!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.16,1:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,明天一大早再见了，大卫\NSee you bright early tomorrow, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.39,1:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，记得要走路哦\NAll right. Hey. Remember to walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.53,1:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢你的帽子，科恩老师\NI really like your hat, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.63,1:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，海瑟，我喜欢你的发型\NWell, thank you, Heather.I like your hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.13,1:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我头发很短是因为我吃的药啦\NIt's just short 'cause of the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.64,1:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.20,1:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝！\NHey, honey!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.51,1:10:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NHi, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.74,1:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以等我一下吗？\NCan you wait right here for just a minute?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.14,1:10:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊  - 好\N-Sure. -OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.28,1:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨，我早就想找你谈海瑟的事了\NHey, umm. I've been meaning to come and speak to you about Heather.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.32,1:10:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想我大概知道\NI think I know....
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.49,1:10:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我们刚开始不想告诉别人\NYeah, umm. We were just reluctant to tell anybody at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.59,1:10:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,当然别人迟早会看到化疗的影响\NOf course it was only a matter of time before the chemo became obvious, so ...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.26,1:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她会好起来吗？\NIs she, ah, going to be okay...?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.20,1:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,海瑟很喜欢上你的课\NUmm. Heather just loves your class.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.17,1:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她每天都等不及要来上学\NShe can't wait to get to school every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.17,1:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能帮我保密更久一点  我会很感激你\NAnd, umm, I'd be grateful if you kept our secret a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.64,1:10:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不希望她被排挤\NI just don't want her to be singled out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.15,1:10:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.45,1:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，好了，宝贝女儿  我们走吧\NThanks. All right, baby girl. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.39,1:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.96,1:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要去吃冰淇淋？\NHow about...an ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.19,1:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.99,1:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.46,1:11:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎样？\NUh-oh. What do you think?What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.03,1:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要，那顶我已经有了\NI already have that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.64,1:11:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但你戴起来很好看\NLooks great on you, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.14,1:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NHey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.08,1:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，我只是专心在想学校的事\NOh, nothing, I'm just focusing on school stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.88,1:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能不能专心在我身上一下？\NCan you focus on me for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.88,1:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.28,1:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！你试戴这顶\NHey, hey, hey! Try this one on!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.62,1:11:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,会让你心情变好\NIt'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.32,1:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好\N-Yeah. -OK. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.89,1:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么样？  - 很好\N- Yeah?    -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.95,1:11:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的？  - 天哪，你戴起来很好看\N-Really?  -Oh my goodness, this suits you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.09,1:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你大概没想到吧\NMore than you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.23,1:11:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定要去修硕士学位了\NI've, ah, decided it's time to go for my master's degree.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.23,1:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.77,1:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是你要搬走了吗？\NWow, does that,does that mean you'll be going away?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.37,1:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，我念本地的学校\NNo. I'd go locally.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.24,1:11:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我要先通过研究所的入学考试啦\NAnyhow, I have to pass the entrance test to graduate school first, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.58,1:11:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，像学力测验那样吗？\NOh, wait. Isn't that like the SATs?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.68,1:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你要和很多人，在一个大房间里考试？\NDo you have to take that in a big room with a lot of people?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.92,1:12:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对，他们说我可以自己一个房间\NYeah. They said I could have a room all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.79,1:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那就好\NAh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.79,1:12:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,图雷特氏症患者是有特权的\NTourette's does have its privileges.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.93,1:12:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我搬走你会难过吗？\NWould it bother you if I did go away...?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.60,1:12:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然会了，你是在开玩笑吧？\NOf course it would. Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.00,1:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 走啦    - 不信你说的\NGet out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.10,1:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 过来，我有东西要给你看         - 神经病\N- Come here, I want to show you something.   - Crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.07,1:12:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位\NNext!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.94,1:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，布莱德·科恩\NHey, ah, chchchch, Brad Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.04,1:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德·科恩\NBrad Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.61,1:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了，科恩先生\NHere you are, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.38,1:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，请你带着这份资料进去\NAll right, I need you take this packet, and I need you to go right in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.21,1:12:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该要有特殊的考场\NOh, I'm supposed to have special accommodations --
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.59,1:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有看到上面有什么标注哦\NI don't have any notation of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.19,1:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说，今天大家都要在同等条件下考试\NI mean, everybody tests under the same conditions today.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.10,1:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我有打电话问过\NOK, yeah, but I called and they said -
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.76,1:12:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说\NThey said-
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.56,1:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说我可以有单独的空间\NThey said that I could have a, ah, space to myself
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.93,1:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧，你去问问负责人\NYou know what? I need you to talk to the administrator about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.76,1:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他的办公室在那边\NHis office is right over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.93,1:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能破例\NI can't make an exception...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.30,1:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没遇过这种事\N...we're not set up that way -
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.97,1:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们同意给我特殊的个人考场\NThey promised and I have the right to special testing accommodations --
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.87,1:13:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有残疾我很抱歉，但我帮不上忙\NListen, I'm sorry about your disability but there isn't anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.98,1:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想参加考试，就得马上进去\Nlf you want to take the test, you need to go in there now --
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.18,1:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看我，有我在那里面，谁还能专心考试？\NLook at me! How could anybody possibly concentrate if I'm in that room?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.95,1:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，现在我得现在开考了\NListen, I have to start the exam, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.12,1:13:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我打电话给你的医生吗？\NDo you need me to call you a doctor...?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.86,1:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你要请谁来帮忙？\NIsn't there anyone you can call for help?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.29,1:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德，冷静点，我没听懂\NBrad, calm down, I can't understand you...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.66,1:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说你可以单独考试？\NWell, they said you could take it alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.17,1:13:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好，没问题，我马上过去\NOK. All right. No problem. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.87,1:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出了什么事吗？\NHas something happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.21,1:13:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以考试了，有单独的考场\NYou can take the test.And you'll have a room to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.68,1:13:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他们说了什么？\NWhat did you say to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.52,1:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,关键字：我要告他们\NThe magic word: lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.79,1:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我该去上班了\NI've gotta get to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.50,1:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿，爸\NHey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.16,1:13:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么事？\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.39,1:13:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.36,1:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你考试顺利\NGood luck on the test.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.43,1:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,事实证明，我需要的不只是爸爸的祝福，我需要的是时间。\NAs it turned out, I needed more than just Dad's good luck. I needed time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.44,1:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,时间有限，我的图雷特氏症不配合\NWith the clock, and my Tourette's, ticking away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.04,1:14:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我来不及把考题全部写完\NI failed to get all the way through the test.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.79,1:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，托马斯，我以你为傲\NGood job, guys.Thomas I am so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.86,1:14:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，科恩老师\NThank you, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.16,1:14:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的火鸡好漂亮，海瑟\NWow! Look at that turkey, Heather.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.23,1:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢老师\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.23,1:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你今年感恩节会过得很热闹吗？\NSo. Are you gonna have a big Thanksgiving this year?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.24,1:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,会啊，妈妈说爷爷奶奶都要来\NUh-huh. Mom says all my grandparents are gonna come.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.67,1:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好特别哦\NWell, that sounds special.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.31,1:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只是他们会哭\N'Cept when they cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.78,1:14:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都偷哭，但我每次都有看到\NThey try to hide itbut I always see them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.38,1:14:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以摸威化吗？\NCan I pet Waffle?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.12,1:14:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然可以摸威化\NYou bet you can pet Waffle.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.55,1:14:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师，你要过感恩节吗？\NAre you gonna have a good Thanksgiving,Mr. Cohen?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.26,1:14:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要啊，我和威化要去圣路易看我妈\NYes, I am. Me and Waffle are going to take a little trip
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.33,1:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,圣路易看我妈\Nto see my Mom in St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.26,1:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道圣路易在哪儿\NI know where that is!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.27,1:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔，太好了，海瑟 - 就是在那里\NWell, that is super, Heather. That's exactly where it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.47,1:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请你帮我一个忙，好吗？\NNow, do me a favor, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.24,1:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要请你照顾我的好朋友威化\NAnd I'm going to trust you to take good care of my friend Waffle. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.24,1:15:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.98,1:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就回来\NAnd I will be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.51,1:15:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，阿曼达，你不用上课吗？\NHi, Amanda. Shouldn't you ja be in your class?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.99,1:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，走吧，我陪你走回教室\NAll right. Come on,I'll walk you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.29,1:15:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我不能在你班上？\NWhy can't I be in your class, Mr. Cohen?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.89,1:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸都是为了你好\NWell, ah. Your father had to do what was best for you, Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.30,1:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你有个很好的老师\NAnd you know what? You've got a great teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.97,1:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，再见了，科恩老师\NOK... See you later, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.79,1:15:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被抓到了\NBusted.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.69,1:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯，那些字你从哪儿学来的？\NWhere did you learn those words, Thomas?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.96,1:16:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没我的同意，你不能离开教室\NYou know you're not supposed to leave the class without asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.90,1:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把门擦干净\NWell, you're going to clean that up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.63,1:16:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我要处罚你不能下课\NAnd then, ah, you're on detention: no recess.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.50,1:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的拼字真是一级棒\NBut you do get an "A" for spelling.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.74,1:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不翻开书就不能念了啊\NYou can't read it if you don't open it, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.88,1:16:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌念书\NI hate reading.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.42,1:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也是\NSo do l.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.62,1:16:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你也是？\NYou do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.75,1:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的，要我念书是很困难的\NYeah. Reading's really hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.02,1:16:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说才不难，你是老师\NIt's not hard for you.You're a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.96,1:16:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要打赌？我们来玩个游戏\NYou wanna bet? Let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.36,1:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,假装你是科恩老师要念书，而我是图雷特氏综合症\NYou be Mr. Cohen trying to read; And I'll be Tourette Syndrome. OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.63,1:16:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你念这一页\NRead this page.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.24,1:16:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“很久以前…”\N"Once upon a time" --
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.94,1:16:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,继续念\NKeep reading.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.34,1:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,“很久以前有一个”…好痒哦\N"...upon a time, there was a" -That itches.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.28,1:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,会痒吗？好了，继续念\NDoes it itch a little bit? All right. Keep reading.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.18,1:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“有一个…”\N"...there was a..."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.18,1:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯！\NHey, Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.42,1:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，很难吧？\NAll right. That's hard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.35,1:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很难专心\NIt's hard to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.02,1:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,念书对我来说就是这么困难\NThat's how hard reading is for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.16,1:17:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说没那么难吧？\NIt's not that hard for you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.29,1:17:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对，对我来说很简单\NNo. It's easy for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.23,1:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你讨厌书要怎么当老师？\NBut...how can you be a teacher if you hate books?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.10,1:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌书？ 我不讨厌书啊，世界上的所有知识都在书里\NHate books? I don't hate books. Everything in the world is in books.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.70,1:17:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我要多费点心力才能学到\NI just have to work extra hard to get it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.91,1:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会放弃你的\NI'm not going to give up on you, buddy. OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.67,1:17:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会让你放弃自己\NAnd I'm not going to let you give up on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.14,1:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,继续念，从这里开始\NNow keep reading. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.21,1:17:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前有个…\N"Once upon a time there was a" --
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.98,1:17:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,魔…魔…\NMag-magi...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.32,1:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法师\NMagician.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.89,1:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“有个魔法师，他遇到一个小男孩\N"A magician who met a small boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.22,1:17:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个小男孩想把一把长剑，从石头里拔出来\NA small boy who was trying to pull a big sword out of a big rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.83,1:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪\NWeird.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.46,1:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,石头里怎么会有剑？\NWhy would a sword be in a rock?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.73,1:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  但你再念下去就会知道了\NWell, I don't know, but if you, ah,keep reading, you might just find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.20,1:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“魔法师跟小男孩说，把剑从石头里拔出来的人\N"The magician told the small boy that whoever could pull the sword out of
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.68,1:18:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就会成为真正的国王”\Nthe rock would be the true king.'' --
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.18,1:18:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好酷哦\NCool.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.19,1:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,继续念啊，后来呢？\NKeep going. What happens next?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.30,1:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,(圣路易，再过12个出口，诺伍广场)
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.07,1:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NHey. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.10,1:18:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我好紧张\NOh, I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.81,1:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好紧张的？你只是去见我妈啊\NWhat's there to be nervous about? You're just gonna meet my Mom -
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.24,1:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢，你还真会安慰人\NThank you. That's, that's helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.98,1:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有杰夫…还有我的舅舅阿姨们…\N-- And Jeff... and my aunts and uncles...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.95,1:18:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我这辈子最爱的每一个亲人\Nand anybody I've ever loved...in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.62,1:19:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你要作好准备，场面会很大\NPrepare your self. This is big.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.06,1:19:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好了，干嘛要我准备？\NI'm ready. Why do I have to prepare myself?.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.99,1:19:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对，你要作好准备\NThat's right. Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.46,1:19:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了啊\NOh, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.67,1:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨！我终于见到南茜了\NOh, hi! I can't believe I'm finally meeting Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.34,1:19:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我想像中更漂亮\NOh! You're even prettier than I thought --
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.34,1:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德经常提到你，科恩太太\NBrad has told me so much about you,Mrs. Cohen -
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.78,1:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我艾伦\NOh, Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.54,1:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他都没什么提到你啦\NWell, that's more than he tells me about you -
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.08,1:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？我经常跟你提到南茜啊\NWha-what! What? I tell you all about Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.21,1:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没告诉我实话啦\NOh, you never tell me the real stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.88,1:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，南茜 - 波波，拿行李\NCome on, Nancy --Bobo, get the bags, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.82,1:19:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对，波波，快去拿\NYes, Bobo. Get on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.49,1:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你累不累？\NSo, are you exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.65,1:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不累\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.32,1:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，因为我们约了一个小时以后要修指甲\NOh, good. Because we've got a pedicure appointment in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.89,1:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.86,1:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这位是南茜     - 嗨\N-This is Nancy.  -Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.29,1:19:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我跟你说的就是她    - 幸会\N- Who I was telling you about. -So, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.63,1:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行，等一下，过来见见珍娜\NAnd, no, wait, Janet. Here, come and meet Janet.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.13,1:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊，嗨   - 南茜，还有一个人…\N-OK. Hi!     - Nancy. And one other person...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.47,1:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈有点过头了  她想给南茜回家的感觉\NMom's going a little overboard making  Nancy feel like family.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.04,1:19:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能吗？她会变成家人吗？\NIs that a possibility? Her being family?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.64,1:19:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，你也知道的\NI don't know. I mean, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.38,1:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不…不…不…\NI know but I don't, I don't,I don't, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.45,1:20:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好，你是认真的。她见过老爸了吗？\NOh, yeah. It's, it's serious. Has she met Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.35,1:20:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，还没有…\NNo! No, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.78,1:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在等什么？\NWell, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.18,1:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,少管闲事啦\NHey. Back off, will'ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.39,1:20:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,结果他跌倒了\N... He ended up falling flat
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.79,1:20:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,头去撞到人行道\Nand then he hit his head straight against the curb.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.73,1:20:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还脑震荡\NGave himself a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.36,1:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪一下，厨房需要南茜\NWell, You'll excuse me, Nancy's needed in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.90,1:20:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要借用她一下\NI'm just going to steal her for one second.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.90,1:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 厨房需要我\NNeeded in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.10,1:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.37,1:20:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你来救我吗？我不需要你救啦\NAre you rescuing me? Because I don't need rescuing --
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.78,1:20:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.38,1:20:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出了什么事？\NWhat's going on -- ?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.08,1:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你修指甲好玩吗？\NHow was your pedicure?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.52,1:20:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想知道\Nlf you're wondering
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.38,1:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你妈聊什么，我们聊的是你啦\Nwhat did your Mom and I talked about, we talked about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.95,1:20:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我们\NAnd us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.56,1:20:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？\NIs something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.33,1:20:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在想\NI was just wondering,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.86,1:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,应不应该告诉你…\Nif I told you,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.83,1:20:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.55,1:21:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我好害怕\NI mean, it just, it scares me. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.61,1:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没想过这件事\NI never thought about it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.68,1:21:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来就不敢去想\NI never dared think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.02,1:21:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德…\NLook, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.12,1:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道你会发出怪声，她不介意\NShe understands about your noises,she doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.86,1:21:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你让她快乐\NYou know, you make her happy, Brad -
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.49,1:21:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是她告诉我的  你逗她笑\Nshe told me that, Brad.You make her laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.50,1:21:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有一天她不笑了怎么办？\NWell, what if one day she stops laughing?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.50,1:21:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有一天她不想再跟我这种…\NWhat if one day she gets fed up of living with someone who -
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.02,1:21:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是…我不想伤害她，妈\NI just, I don't want to hurt her,Mom....
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.66,1:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是你不想受伤吧\NMaybe you don't want to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.43,1:21:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,都有啦\NBoth.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.43,1:22:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一件事会伤害你们\NThe only thing that can hurt either of you:
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.30,1:22:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你让图雷特氏症把她赶走\Nis if you let Tourette's drive her away from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.14,1:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要被它打败\Nlf you let it win.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.08,1:22:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,海瑟的妈妈打电话来\NHeather's mother had called to say
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.48,1:22:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说海瑟没办法再上学了\NHeather was no longer able to attend school.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.35,1:22:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,全班同学都在想办法替她打气\NSo, the class all pitched in to cheer her up --
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.95,1:22:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看这张桌子\NOh, wow. Look at this table.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.86,1:22:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很棒嘛\NIt looks very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.09,1:22:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这个看起来也很棒\NAh, this looks great over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.45,1:22:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,(我爱海瑟)
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.74,1:22:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(海瑟)
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.01,1:22:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,过了几个礼拜  我们大家害怕的消息来了\NThe news we'd all been dreading came a few weeks later....
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.06,1:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.70,1:22:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨，科恩老师\NHi, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.80,1:22:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好，亨利\NWhat's up, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.20,1:22:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.30,1:22:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨，伊莱  - 嗨，科恩老师\N-Hey, Eli. -Hi, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.07,1:22:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨，科恩老师\NHey, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.84,1:23:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好，盖伦\NWhat's up, Gaylon?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.97,1:23:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我爷爷奶奶 詹姆斯和雪莉\NThese are my grandparents,James and Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.82,1:23:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,仪式就要开始了\NSir, they're about to start the service.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.66,1:23:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你先进去吧\NYou go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.97,1:23:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师？ 你不进来吗？\NMr. Cohen? Aren't you coming in?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.40,1:23:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉，我很想进去\NI'm sorry... I thought I could but I...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.31,1:23:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但我会干扰仪式的进行\NI think I'd be too disruptive.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.84,1:23:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你改变了海瑟的一生\NYou made such a huge difference in Heather's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.98,1:23:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你是她最喜欢的老师\NYou were her favorite teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.32,1:23:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请你务必送她最后一程\NPlease, don't leave without saying goodbye to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.64,1:24:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,(复活节快乐)
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.71,1:24:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(乔治亚州)
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.32,1:24:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，托马斯，你那一组的词叫什么？\NOkay, Thomas... what is your team's word?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.95,1:24:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“怪胎”\NWeird!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.29,1:25:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,“怪胎”。不是托马斯那一组的人，有谁知道“怪胎”是什么意思？\NWeird. Anybody not on Thomas's team know what that word means?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.66,1:25:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪\NStrange.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.63,1:25:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,诡异\NCreepy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.96,1:25:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怖\NScary.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.96,1:25:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NVery good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.93,1:25:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁会用“奇怪”造句？\NWho can use the word weird in a sentence?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.77,1:25:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我！我！\NMe, oh, me!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.20,1:25:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,25、30、35、40。绑辫子的女生，50！盖伦！\N25, 30, 35, 40. The girl in pigtails. 50! Gaylon!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.81,1:25:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“我喜欢奇怪的电影”。抱歉，科恩老师\N"I like weird movies." Sorry, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.68,1:25:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不能去看电影\NI know you can't go to them
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.98,1:25:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你会被戏院赶出来\Nbecause you get thrown out of the movie theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.91,1:25:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，盖伦\NWell, that's OK, Gaylon.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.85,1:25:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我可以租片子回家看\NBoom. Because I can rent movies.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.18,1:25:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我喜欢奇怪的电影\NAnd I also like weird movies.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.65,1:25:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以“奇怪”是个好字\NSo weird is a good word, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.52,1:25:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可如果有人跟你说：“喂！”\NBut what if someone comes up to you and they say,"Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.83,1:25:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,“你，我在跟你讲话。你好奇怪”\NYeah, you. I'm talking to you. You're weird.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.00,1:25:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这时它还是个好词吗？\NIs it still a good word?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.40,1:25:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是\NNoooo.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.97,1:25:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音？\NWhat, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.74,1:25:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，大家都回座位上坐好\NOK, everyone, stay in your seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.74,1:25:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是玛克辛和大红卡车\NIt's Maxine and big Red.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.88,1:25:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师，我们可以去看吗？\NMr. Cohen, can't we go see them?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.52,1:25:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好，但大家都要小声一点\NOkay, but everyone... inside voices...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.05,1:25:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,到门口排好队，不准用跑的\NEveryone line up by the door and no running.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.34,1:26:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题。好啊。伊莱，上去啊\NYou got it. Yeah. Exactly. Eli, get in there, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.55,1:26:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，但你要小心\NAll right, but be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.36,1:26:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎样？满酷的吧？\NSo, what do you think of it?Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.59,1:26:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱，我不是说了吗？好了，不准按喇叭\NEli! What did I tell you? All right, no pulling the horn.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.76,1:26:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,否则就全部都下来\NOr else you guys are coming down.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.76,1:26:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，玛克辛\NSorry, Maxine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.47,1:26:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦\NThat's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.10,1:26:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩就是小孩\NKids will be kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.34,1:26:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对，永远是这样\NYes, yeah. Yeah, they will.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.14,1:26:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们相处得还好吧？\NThey still getting along?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.71,1:27:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是不错\NWell, it looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.68,1:27:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们一点时间\NGive 'em time.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.92,1:27:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢南茜\NI like Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.72,1:27:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她让我想起我当年刚认识的你妈\NShe reminds me of your Mom when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.16,1:27:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她们长得一点也不像\NThey don't look anything alike.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.73,1:27:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我指的不是长相，而是…\NI'm not talking about looks;I'm talking about that...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.50,1:27:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那种活力，很难形容啦\Nspark, that spirit,that, ah, "je ne sais quoi."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.30,1:27:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,学校还好吗？\NHow are things at school?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.97,1:27:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\NOh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.04,1:27:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,书太多，书柜不够放，屋顶漏水，预算删减\NWe got more books than bookcases, roof leaks, budget cutbacks...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.81,1:27:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真有点担心他们明年不会续聘我\NLittle worried they might not ask me back next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.45,1:27:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多老师比我经验更丰富\NThere's plenty of teachers with a lot more experience than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.65,1:27:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样，我都以你为傲\NI'm proud of you regardless.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.89,1:27:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉不到\NDoesn't feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.69,1:27:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我觉得你还是因为我而不太痛快？\NWhy do I feel like you're still embarrassed by me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.49,1:27:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，爸，你大可承认\NAnd it's okay, Dad, you can admit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.10,1:27:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你又想吵架吗？\NYou're not trying to start something...?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.00,1:27:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是…\NNo. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.10,1:27:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们终于讲话了，这样很好，那就来聊吧\NBut, you know, we're finally talking, and it's good, so let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.94,1:27:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直让你觉得丢脸\NI've always been an embarrassment to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.61,1:28:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对？你以前来看我\NI have, haven't l? Even when you used to come visit me,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.44,1:28:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别人盯着我看，你还是介意\Nyou used to squirm when all those eyeballs would click my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.61,1:28:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你从来就无法接受\NYou've never been able to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.29,1:28:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.79,1:28:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候跟你在一起很难受\NIt is tough being with you sometimes -
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.99,1:28:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我最讨厌跟你去餐厅，大家都用那种眼神看你\NI hate it when we go to restaurants and people give you those looks.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.83,1:28:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候我…\NSometimes, I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.00,1:28:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得好无助\NI just feel so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.01,1:28:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都在帮别人修东西\NYou know, I've always been a guy who could fix things...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.74,1:28:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但有样东西我一直修不好\N...but the one thing I could never fix was the one thing
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.54,1:28:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是伤你最深的东西\Nthat was hurting you most.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.38,1:28:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这不需要修啦\NIt doesn't need fixing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.68,1:28:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能修好\NNobody can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.42,1:28:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\NI know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.69,1:28:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但也许是我的错\NBut maybe it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.93,1:28:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是我遗传给你的\NMaybe I gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.51,1:29:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这些肉应该熟了\NI think these babies are done.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.98,1:29:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\NCome on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.44,1:29:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体中心再过两分钟，就要关了\NWe only have two minutes before the media center closes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.71,1:29:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,后面的跟上来，靠旁边走\NHurry up, back there. Stay to the side, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.62,1:29:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,靠旁边走…我不是讲了吗？后面的快一点，跟上来\NStay to the side. What did I tell you?Guys in the back, come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.49,1:29:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爸？\NDad?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.16,1:29:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会来这里？\NWhat are you, ah,what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.89,1:29:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说学校缺书柜吗？\NYou said you needed bookcases,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.36,1:29:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸要帮我们的图书馆钉书柜\NYour Father's built us new bookshelves for the library.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.97,1:29:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,流程跑起来有点慢啦\NThings are a little slow at the office.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.17,1:29:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请\NThis way, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.77,1:29:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有样东西要给你\NOh, and I got you something for your collection.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.51,1:29:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师，你快戴啊\NPut it on, Mr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.22,1:29:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,硬帽子戴在顽固的脑袋上面\NA hard hat for an extremely hard head.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.56,1:30:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同学，他是我爸爸\NHey, class, that's my dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.13,1:30:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨，科恩先生\NHi, Mr. Cohen!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.20,1:30:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨\NHi!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.44,1:30:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.47,1:30:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.24,1:30:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉里没说是为了什么事？\NAnd, and Hilarie didn't say what this was about?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.24,1:30:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NNo idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.78,1:30:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正好下课，她说要来你的教室找你\NWe were at recess and she said she needs to see you in your classroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.05,1:30:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是和明年的事有关吧\NI think it might have to do with next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.39,1:30:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了\NHere he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.96,1:30:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱德\NBrad.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.42,1:30:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请你过来一下，好吗？\NWould you come over here a moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.49,1:30:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,希拉里有事要宣布\NHilarie's got an announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.63,1:30:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人可能注意到\NSome of you may have noticed
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.03,1:30:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最近几个礼拜，有个人一直在学校里旁观\Nan observer hanging around school the last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.90,1:30:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来评估我们的一位老师\NWell, he was here to assess one of our teachers.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.01,1:30:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师\NMr. Cohen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.78,1:30:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要宣布我们的科恩老师\NAnd I'm here to announce that our very own Brad Cohen has been chosen
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.88,1:31:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在乔治亚州的教育界，新教育工作者中脱颖而出\Nfrom amongst all the new educators in the state of
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.25,1:31:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,获选为本年度的最佳教师\NGeorgia to be Sallie Mae's First Year Teacher of the Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.43,1:31:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着我的学生们，我觉得自己也像个小孩\NAs I looked at my students, I felt like a kid inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.44,1:31:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为小孩看待人生的观点和多数的成年人不一样\NBecause children look at life differently than most audits.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.71,1:31:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看着这个世界，会说我要做，不是我做不到，我也一样\NThey see the world and say, I will.Not I can't. And so did l.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.65,1:31:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这件衬衫太紧了，标签刺得我的背好痛\NThis shirt's too tight.The label's digging in my back...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.42,1:31:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,标签我剪掉了，真搞不懂你有什么好紧张的\NI cut out the label. I don't know what you're so nervous about.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.36,1:31:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你每天都在面对群众啊\NYou're in front of a crowd every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.03,1:31:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人可不是二年级的小孩\NWell, these aren't second-graders.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.83,1:31:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在...\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.40,1:31:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪，真希望我可以隐形\NOh, man, I wish I was invisible.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.47,1:31:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这你就永远不必担心了\NWell, that is something you'll never have to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.57,1:31:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动…\NHold still, hold still!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.61,1:31:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.22,1:32:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,科恩老师加油！\NGo, Mr. Cohen!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.71,1:32:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,加油，波波，你一定可以的\NCome on, Bobo,you can get through this --
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.05,1:32:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧，他绝对没问题\NDon't worry.He's going to get through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.82,1:32:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们刚才听到的怪声\NThe noise you just heard is the Tourette Syndrome
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.35,1:32:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我从6岁就得的图雷特氏症\NI've been living with since I was six years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.36,1:32:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天站在这里，是因为有很多人的爱与支持\NI'm standing up here today because the love and support of a lot of people put me up here -
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.97,1:32:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的家人\NMy family,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.97,1:33:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我学校的大家庭，我的学生和所有好朋友\Nmy school family,my students, and all my friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.37,1:33:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这个奖要归功给他们\NI owe this award to all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.94,1:33:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也要感谢我这辈子\NBut I also owe it to the toughest,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.48,1:33:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,最难搞、也最执着的老师\Nand, and most dedicated teacher I ever had:
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.58,1:33:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我忠实的伙伴，图雷特氏症\Nmy Constant Companion. My Tourette's.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.39,1:33:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可能会觉得不可思议，怎么会感谢一种残疾\NNow, some of you may think that's pretty weird to thank a disability...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.73,1:33:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还称之为好老师？\Nand calling it a great teacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.99,1:33:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这的确很奇怪\NThat's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.23,1:33:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指，我从残疾中学到了什么呢？\NI mean, what could I possibly learn from a disability?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.61,1:33:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,盖伦，请说\NYes, Gaylon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.01,1:33:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你学会了坚持到底\NYou learned to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.45,1:33:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱？\NEli?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.65,1:33:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你学会了不让残疾阻止你\NYou learned to not let it stop you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.16,1:33:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯，请说\NYes, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.16,1:33:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你学会了不被残疾打倒\NYou learned to not let it win!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.90,1:34:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,答对了\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.77,1:34:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,应对我的图雷特氏症让我学到任何人都从未学过的、最有价值的一课\NCoping with my Tourette's has taught me the most valuable lesson that anyone could ever learn:
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.88,1:34:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是千万别让任何事阻止你去追逐梦想\NAnd that is to never let anything stop you from chasing your dream;
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.18,1:34:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止你工作，或是寻找乐趣，或是坠入爱河\Nfrom working or playing or falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.49,1:34:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.33,1:34:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,应对我的图雷特氏症让我学到了这个最宝贵的一课…\NCoping with my Tourette's has taught me the most valuable lesson....
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.57,1:34:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯，请说\NYes, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.00,1:34:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你礼拜一上课能不能带奖牌，去讲故事给我们听？\NCan you bring that award to show and tell on Monday?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.41,1:34:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NYou bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.52,1:35:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,(布莱德后来拿到了硕士学位)
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.06,1:35:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(他也实现了毕生的愿望)
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.80,1:35:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,(扮成“荷马”亚特兰大勇士队的吉祥物)
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.23,1:35:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,(布莱德和南茜在2006年结婚)
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.04,1:35:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,(他们住在亚特兰大)
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.14,1:35:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(这是真实生活中的布莱德·科恩)
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.02,1:35:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,(他一直做着他最喜欢的)
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.18,1:35:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(教育工作)
